## <a name="authentication-events"></a><span data-ttu-id="72c2f-159">Događaji provjere autentičnosti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-159">Authentication events</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-160">Ti se događaji dijagnostičkih podataka prikupljaju kada Office pokuša dohvatiti token za provjeru autentičnosti, bilo u pozadini ili putem upita korisniku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-160">These diagnostic data events are collected when Office attempts to acquire an authentication token, either silently or through prompting.</span></span>

### <a name="officeandroidmsaguesttoaad"></a><span data-ttu-id="72c2f-161">Office.Android.MSAGuestToAAD</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-161">Office.Android.MSAGuestToAAD</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-162">Ovaj događaj pomaže razumjeti od koliko je korisnika zatraženo davanje lozinke za osobni račun tijekom pristupanja poslovnim resursima, jer bi njihov osobni račun mogao biti valjan gost klijentu poslovnog računa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-162">This event helps in understanding how many users are getting prompted for providing personal account password, while accessing work resource, as their personal account could be a valid guest to work account's tenant.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-163">Ovi podaci nam pomažu razumjeti koliko korisnika prolazi kroz muke prijave u ponovnim upitima radi davanja prioriteta tihom pribavljanju AAD tokena na temelju SAML (Jezik za označavanje sigurnosnih izraza) izraza Microsoftovog računa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-163">This data helps us understand how many users are going through the pain of sign in re-prompts to prioritize AAD token acquisition silently based on a Microsoft account SAML (Security Assertion Markup Language) assertion.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-164">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-164">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-165">**Tag** - Označava da je korisnik dobio upit za prijavu za osobni račun tijekom pristupanja resursima poslovnog računa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-165">**Tag** - Indicates that user got sign-in prompt for personal account, while accessing work account resource.</span></span>


### <a name="officeidentityfbapromptwin32"></a><span data-ttu-id="72c2f-166">Office.Identity.FbaPromptWin32</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-166">Office.Identity.FbaPromptWin32</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-167">Prikuplja se kada Office korisniku prikaže upit za prijavu pomoću provjere autentičnosti na temelju obrazaca.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-167">Collected when Office shows the user a Forms-Based-Auth sign-in prompt.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-168">Upiti za provjeru autentičnosti zajedno s pozadinskim pribavljanjem tokena koriste se za utvrđivanje je li korisnik u neispravnom stanju provjere autentičnosti, koje se za korisnika očituje praktički izvanmrežnim stanjem klijenta. Neispravna provjera autentičnosti može i onemogućiti dohvaćanje licence, što uzrokuje potpunu nemogućnost korištenja klijenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-168">Along with silent token acquisitions, authentication prompts are used to determine if user is in a broken authentication state which, for the user, results in what is essentially an Offline Client state, or in the worst case, broken authentication may prevent license acquisition and result in a completely unusable client.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-169">Upiti za prijavu pomoću provjere autentičnosti na temelju obrazaca (FBA) upotrebljavaju se u nekim scenarijima lokalne provjere autentičnosti i najčešće ne želimo da se to događa jer bi svi trebali koristiti modernu provjeru autentičnosti zbog sigurnosnih slabih točaka povezanih s provjerom autentičnosti na temelju obrazaca.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-169">Forms-Based-Auth (FBA) sign-in prompts are used for some on-premises authentication scenarios and typically we want to make sure this isn't happening, as everyone should be using Modern-Auth because of security vulnerabilities associated with FBA.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-170">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-170">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-171">**AuthScheme** – korištena shema provjere autentičnosti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-171">**AuthScheme** - the authentication scheme used</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-172">**DocumentUrlHash** – šifrirano slanje zahtjeva za URL</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-172">**DocumentUrlHash** - an encrypted URL requesting</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-173">**EndTag** – oznaka ispunjenosti FPA obrasca</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-173">**EndTag** - the tag where FBA form is completed</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-174">**Flags** – zastarjelo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-174">**Flags** - Obsolete</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-175">**FlowTag** – oznaka pokretanja FBA obrasca</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-175">**FlowTag** - the tag where FBA form is started</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-176">**LastError** – vraćena šifra pogreške</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-176">**LastError** – the error code returned</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-177">**PromptEndTime** – vrijeme završetka upita</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-177">**PromptEndTime** - the time when then prompt ended</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-178">**PromptStartTime** – vrijeme početka upita</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-178">**PromptStartTime** - the time when the prompt started</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-179">**Result** – označava je li provjera autentičnosti uspjela</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-179">**Result** - whether the authentication succeeded</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-180">**SessionEndTime** – vrijeme završetka sesije događaja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-180">**SessionEndTime** – the time when the event session ended</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-181">**Timeout** – vrijeme isteka vremena upita</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-181">**Timeout** - the time when the prompt timed out</span></span>

### <a name="officeidentitysignoutevent"></a><span data-ttu-id="72c2f-182">Office.Identity.SignOutEvent</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-182">Office.Identity.SignOutEvent</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-183">Prikuplja se kad se korisnik odjavi iz sustava Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-183">Collected when a user signs out of Office.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-184">Kad se zna da se korisnik odjavio, moguće je na očekivani način klasificirati druge događaje, kao što su upiti, da bi se točno izračunali u metrici pouzdanosti / spremnosti za isporuku te se izbjegavaju upozorenja ili vraćanje međuverzija na temelju pogrešne premise da se korisniku prikazuju neočekivani upiti za prijavu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-184">Knowing the user is signed-out makes it possible to classify other events, such as prompts, as expected, so those events can be correctly computed in reliability / ship-readiness metrics and avoid alerting or rolling back builds on the faulty premise that the user is experiencing unexpected sign-in prompts.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-185">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-185">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-186">**FlowEndTime** – vrijeme završetka radnje odjave</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-186">**FlowEndTime** - the time when the sign out action ended</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-187">**FlowStartTime** – vrijeme početka radnje odjave</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-187">**FlowStartTime** - the time when the sign out action started</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-188">**IdentityErrorState** – bilo koje stanje pogreške identiteta tijekom odjave</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-188">**IdentityErrorState** - any identity error state during sign out</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-189">**IdentityHashedUniqueId** – šifrirani ID identiteta koji se odjavljuje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-189">**IdentityHashedUniqueId** - the encrypted identity ID being signed out</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-190">**IdentityProviderType** – davatelj identiteta koji se odjavljuje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-190">**IdentityProviderType** - the identity provider of the identity being signed out</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-191">**IdentityUniqueID** – ID identiteta koji se odjavljuje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-191">**IdentityUniqueID** - the identity ID being signed out</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-192">**SessionEndTime** – vrijeme završetka sesije događaja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-192">**SessionEndTime** - the time when the event session ended</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-193">**SignOutUserAction** – označava da je korisnik pokrenuo radnju odjave</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-193">**SignOutUserAction** - Indicates the user initiates the sign out action</span></span>

### <a name="officeidentitysspipromptwin32"></a><span data-ttu-id="72c2f-194">Office.Identity.SspiPromptWin32</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-194">Office.Identity.SspiPromptWin32</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-195">Prikuplja se kada Office korisniku prikaže upit za prijavu putem Windows SSPI-ja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-195">Collected when Office shows the user a Windows SSPI sign-in prompt.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-196">Upiti za provjeru autentičnosti zajedno s pozadinskim pribavljanjem tokena određuju je li korisnik u neispravnom stanju provjere autentičnosti, koje se očituje izvanmrežnim stanjem klijenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-196">Along with silent token acquisitions, authentication prompts determine whether a user is in a broken authentication state, which results in an Offline Client state.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-197">Neispravna provjera autentičnosti može i onemogućiti dohvaćanje licence, što uzrokuje potpunu nemogućnost korištenja klijenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-197">Broken authentication may prevent license acquisition and result in a completely unusable client.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-198">Upiti Windows SSPI-ja koriste se za provjeru autentičnosti u sustavu Exchange (za sinkronizaciju pošte) kad korisnikov resurs sustava Exchange nije postavljen za višestruku provjeru autentičnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-198">Windows SSPI prompts are used for authenticating with Exchange (for mail synchronizing) when the user's Exchange resource hasn't been set up for multi-factor authentication.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-199">Ti događaji, zajedno s događajima prostora za naziv Office.MATS, koriste se u sljedeće svrhe:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-199">These events, along with the Office.MATS namespace events, are used for the following purposes:</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-200">1\) utvrđivanje mogu li klijenti uspješno dohvatiti token za provjeru autentičnosti ili su prešli u stanje neispravne provjere autentičnosti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-200">1\) Identify whether clients can successfully obtain an authentication token or have entered a broken authentication state.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-201">2\) procjenu jesu li promjene u klijentu ili servisu uzrokovale kritično nazadovanje sučelja i pouzdanosti provjere autentičnosti korisnika</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-201">2\) Evaluate whether changes that have occurred on the client or services have resulted in critical regressions in the user's authentication experience and reliability</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-202">3\) u slučaju pogrešaka ti signali šalju važne šifre pogrešaka iz odgovorne komponente (koda klijentskog programa sustava Office, biblioteka za provjeru autentičnosti ili servisa izdavatelja certifikata) koje se mogu koristiti za klasifikaciju hitnosti, dijagnozu i otklanjanje problema</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-202">3\) When failures occur, these signals emit important failure codes from the responsible component (Office client code, authentication libraries, or authority services) which can be used for triage, diagnosis and mitigation</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-203">4\) signali služe kao podaci za razne nadzornike spremnosti za isporuku i stanja koji aktiviraju upozorenja da bi se naši inženjeri mogli brzo angažirati i skratiti vrijeme do otklanjanje kritičnih pogrešaka koje blokiraju rad korisnika</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-203">4\) These signals power various ship readiness and health monitors which fire alerts so our engineers can engage quickly and reduce the time to mitigation of critical user-blocking failures</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-204">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-204">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-205">**AllowSavedCreds** – jesu li nove vjerodajnice trajno pohranjene</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-205">**AllowSavedCreds** - whether the new credential is persisted</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-206">**AuthScheme** – korištena shema provjere autentičnosti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-206">**AuthScheme** - the authentication scheme used</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-207">**CredsSaved** – jesu li nove vjerodajnice spremljene</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-207">**CredsSaved** - whether the new credential is saved</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-208">**DocumentUrlHash** – šifrirano slanje zahtjeva za URL</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-208">**DocumentUrlHash** - the encrypted URL requesting</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-209">**EndTag** – oznaka završetka upita</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-209">**EndTag** - the tag where the prompt ended</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-210">**NewIdentity**\_ErrorState – označava je li novi identitet valjan</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-210">**NewIdentity**\_ErrorState – whether the new identity is valid</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-211">**NewIdentity\_HashedUniqueId** – šifrirani ID novog identiteta nakon dovršetka upita</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-211">**NewIdentity\_HashedUniqueId** - the encrypted new identity ID after prompt is completed</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-212">**NewIdentity\_ProviderType** – davatelj novog identiteta nakon dovršetka upita</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-212">**NewIdentity\_ProviderType** - the new identity provider after the prompt is completed</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-213">**NewIdentity\_UniqueID** – ID novog identiteta nakon dovršetka upita</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-213">**NewIdentity\_UniqueID** - the new identity ID after the prompt is completed</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-214">**OutStatus** – označava je li rezultat upita valjan</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-214">**OutStatus** - whether the prompt output is valid</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-215">**PromptEndTime** – vrijeme završetka upita</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-215">**PromptEndTime** - the time when the prompt ended</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-216">**PromptFailedTag** – oznaka da SSPI upit nije uspio</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-216">**PromptFailedTag** - the tag that indicates SSPI prompt failure</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-217">**PromptFlow** – oznaka koja je aktivirala SSPI upit</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-217">**PromptFlow** - the tag that invoked the SSPI prompt</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-218">**PromptStartTime** – vrijeme početka upita</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-218">**PromptStartTime** - the time when the prompt started</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-219">**Proxy** – označava koristi li se proxy</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-219">**Proxy** - if proxy is used</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-220">**ServerHash** – šifrirana adresa poslužitelja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-220">**ServerHash** - the encrypted server address</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-221">**SessionEndTime** – vrijeme završetka sesije događaja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-221">**SessionEndTime** - the time when the event session ended</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-222">**Timeout** – vrijeme isteka vremena upita</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-222">**Timeout** - the time when the prompt is timed out</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-223">**UiMessage** – poruka korisničkog sučelja u upitu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-223">**UiMessage** - the UI message in the prompt</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-224">**UserNameHash** – šifrirano korisničko ime</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-224">**UserNameHash** - the encrypted user name</span></span>

### <a name="officeidentitywin32prompt"></a><span data-ttu-id="72c2f-225">Office.Identity.Win32Prompt</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-225">Office.Identity.Win32Prompt</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-226">Prikuplja se kada Office korisniku prikaže upit za prijavu putem višestruke provjere autentičnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-226">Collected when Office shows the user a multi-factor authentication sign-in prompt.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-227">Upiti za provjeru autentičnosti zajedno s pozadinskim pribavljanjem tokena određuju je li korisnik u neispravnom stanju provjere autentičnosti, koje se očituje izvanmrežnim stanjem klijenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-227">Along with silent token acquisitions, authentication prompts determine whether a user is in a broken authentication state, which results in an Offline Client state.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-228">Neispravna provjera autentičnosti može i onemogućiti dohvaćanje licence, što uzrokuje potpunu nemogućnost korištenja klijenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-228">Broken authentication may prevent license acquisition and result in a completely unusable client.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-229">Ti događaji, zajedno s događajima prostora za naziv Office.MATS, koriste se u sljedeće svrhe:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-229">These events, along with the Office.MATS namespace events, are used for the following purposes:</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-230">1\) utvrđivanje mogu li klijenti uspješno dohvatiti token za provjeru autentičnosti ili su prešli u stanje neispravne provjere autentičnosti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-230">1\) Identify whether clients can successfully obtain an authentication token or have entered in to a broken authentication state.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-231">2\) procjenu jesu li promjene u klijentu ili servisu uzrokovale kritično nazadovanje sučelja i pouzdanosti provjere autentičnosti korisnika</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-231">2\) Evaluate whether changes that have occurred on the client or services have resulted in critical regressions in the user's authentication experience and reliability</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-232">3\) u slučaju pogrešaka ti signali šalju važne šifre pogrešaka iz odgovorne komponente (koda klijentskog programa sustava Office, biblioteka za provjeru autentičnosti ili servisa izdavatelja certifikata) koje se mogu koristiti za klasifikaciju hitnosti, dijagnozu i otklanjanje problema</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-232">3\) When failures occur, these signals emit important failure codes from the responsible component (Office client code, authentication libraries, or authority services) which can be used for triage, diagnosis and mitigation</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-233">4\) signali služe kao podaci za razne nadzornike spremnosti za isporuku i stanja koji aktiviraju upozorenja da bi se naši inženjeri mogli brzo angažirati i skratiti vrijeme do otklanjanje kritičnih pogrešaka koje blokiraju rad korisnika</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-233">4\) These signals power various ship readiness and health monitors which fire alerts so our engineers can engage quickly and reduce the time to mitigation of critical user-blocking failures.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-234">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-234">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-235">**AdalWAMUsed** – oznaka rezultata ako je korišten ADAL-atop-WAM</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-235">**AdalWAMUsed** – the tag that indicates result if ADAL-atop-WAM is used</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-236">**CallTag** – oznaka pozivatelja korisničkog sučelja za prijavu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-236">**CallTag** – the tag that indicates the caller of sign in UI</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-237">**Context** – kontekst prijave za upit</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-237">**Context** - the sign in context for the prompt</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-238">**EndTagIdentityProviderRequested** – oznaka da je zatražen davatelj identiteta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-238">**EndTagIdentityProviderRequested** - the tag where the identity provider is requested</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-239">**HrdShownTag** – oznaka da je prikazan HRD dijaloški okvir za prijavu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-239">**HrdShownTag** - the tag where the HRD sign in dialog is shown</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-240">**IdentityProviderResulted** – zatražena vrsta davatelja identiteta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-240">**IdentityProviderResulted** - the identity provider type it is requesting</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-241">**IdPFlowTag** – označava rezultat zahtjeva za identitet</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-241">**IdPFlowTag** - the tag that indicates the identity request result</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-242">**LastLoginDelta** – delta vremena od zadnje uspješne prijave</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-242">**LastLoginDelta** - the time delta from last successful login</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-243">**NewIdentity\_ErrorState** – označava je li identitet valjan nakon upita</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-243">**NewIdentity\_ErrorState** - whether the identity is valid after prompt</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-244">**NewIdentity\_ProviderType** – vrsta davatelja novog identiteta nakon upita</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-244">**NewIdentity\_ProviderType** - the new identity provider type after prompt</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-245">**NewIdentity\_UniqueID** – vraćeni ID novog identiteta nakon upita</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-245">**NewIdentity\_UniqueID** - the new identity ID returned after prompt</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-246">**PromptCorrelation** – ID korelacije upita za dijagnostičke svrhe</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-246">**PromptCorrelation** - the prompt correlation ID for diagnostic purpose</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-247">**PromptEndTime** – vrijeme završetka upita</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-247">**PromptEndTime** - the time when the prompt ended</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-248">**PromptStartTime** – vrijeme početka upita</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-248">**PromptStartTime** – the time when the prompt started</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-249">**SessionEndTime** – vrijeme završetka sesije događaja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-249">**SessionEndTime** - the time when the event session ended</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-250">**ShowUIResult** – šifra rezultata koju je vratilo korisničko sučelje upita</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-250">**ShowUIResult** – the result code returned from the prompt UI</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-251">**StartTag** – oznaka da je pokrenut Win32 upit</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-251">**StartTag** – the tag where Win32 prompt started</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-252">**Timeout** – vrijeme isteka vremena upita</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-252">**Timeout** - the time when the prompt is timed out</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-253">**WasIdentitySignedOut** – označava je li korisnik odjavljen</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-253">**WasIdentitySignedOut** - whether the user is signed out</span></span>

### <a name="officematsactionofficewin32-officematsactionofficewinrt"></a><span data-ttu-id="72c2f-254">Office.MATS.actionofficewin32, Office.MATS.actionofficewinrt</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-254">Office.MATS.actionofficewin32, Office.MATS.actionofficewinrt</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-255">Sljedeći se opis odnosi i na Win32 događaje i na WinRT događaje (naziv ovisi o platformi)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-255">The following description applies for both Win32 and WinRT events (the name depends on platform.)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-256">Microsoft Auth Telemetry System (MATS) prikuplja se kada Office pokuša dohvatiti token za provjeru autentičnosti, bilo u pozadini ili putem upita korisniku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-256">Microsoft Auth Telemetry System (MATS) is collected when Office attempts to acquire an authentication token, either silently or through prompting.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-257">Kada pokušaj dohvaćanja ne uspije, uvrštavaju se informacije o pogrešci.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-257">When acquisition attempts fail, error information is included.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-258">Korisnici pomoću tih događaja mogu izbjeći prelazak u stanje neispravne provjere autentičnosti tako što:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-258">These events help our users avoid entering broken authentication states by:</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-259">1\) utvrde mogu li klijenti uspješno dohvatiti token za provjeru autentičnosti ili su prešli u stanje neispravne provjere autentičnosti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-259">1\) Identifying whether clients can successfully obtain an authentication token or have entered a broken authentication state.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-260">2\) procijene uzrokuju li promjene u klijentu ili servisu kritično nazadovanje sučelja i pouzdanosti provjere autentičnosti korisnika</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-260">2\) Evaluate when changes occur on the client or services, whether they result in critical regressions in the user's authentication experience and reliability</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-261">3\) u slučaju pogrešaka ti signali šalju važne šifre pogrešaka iz odgovorne komponente (koda klijentskog programa sustava Office, biblioteka za provjeru autentičnosti ili servisa izdavatelja certifikata) koje se mogu koristiti za klasifikaciju hitnosti, dijagnozu i otklanjanje problema</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-261">3\) When failures occur, these signals emit important failure codes from the responsible component (Office client code, authentication libraries, or authority services) which can be used for triage, diagnosis and mitigation</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-262">4\) signali služe kao podaci za razne nadzornike spremnosti za isporuku i stanja koji aktiviraju upozorenja da bi se naši inženjeri mogli brzo angažirati i skratiti vrijeme do otklanjanje kritičnih pogrešaka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-262">4\) These signals power various ship readiness and health monitors which fire alerts so our engineers can engage quickly and reduce the time to mitigation of critical failures.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-263">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-263">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-264">**Actiontype** – označava koja se biblioteka provjere autentičnosti koristi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-264">**Actiontype** - Which authentication library is used</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-265">**Appaudience** – označava je li međuverzija aplikacije za internu ili vanjsku upotrebu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-265">**Appaudience** - Is the app build for internal or external use</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-266">**Appforcedprompt** – označava je li aplikacija nadjačala predmemoriju i prisilno prikazala upit</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-266">**Appforcedprompt** - Did the app override cache and force a prompt to be shown</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-267">**Appname** – naziv aplikacije koja provodi provjeru autentičnosti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-267">**Appname** - Name of the application doing authentication</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-268">**Appver** – verzija aplikacije koja provodi provjeru autentičnosti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-268">**Appver** - Version of the application doing authentication</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-269">**Askedforcreds** – označava je li aplikacija od korisnika tražila unos vjerodajnica za tu radnju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-269">**Askedforcreds** - Did the application ask the user to enter credentials for this action</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-270">**Authoutcome** – označava uspjeh, neuspjeh ili otkazivanje provjere autentičnosti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-270">**Authoutcome** - Did the authentication attempt succeed, fail, or was canceled</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-271">**Blockingprompt** – označava je li aplikacija izbacila upit na koji korisnik mora reagirati</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-271">**Blockingprompt** - Did the application throw a prompt requiring user interaction</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-272">**Correlationid** – GUID korišten za spajanje sa servisnim podacima</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-272">**Correlationid** - GUID used for joining with services data</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-273">**Count** – broj događaja u slučajevima agregacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-273">**Count** - Count of events in cases of aggregation</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-274">**Data\_accounttype** – označava je li u pitanju osobni račun ili račun tvrtke ili ustanove</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-274">**Data\_accounttype** - Consumer or organizational account</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-275">**Devicenetworkstate** – označava je li korisnik bio na mreži</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-275">**Devicenetworkstate** - Was the user online</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-276">**Deviceprofiletelemetryid** – anonimni ID uređaja koji se koristi za mjerenje iskustva na uređaju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-276">**Deviceprofiletelemetryid** - Anonymous device ID used to measure device experience</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-277">**Duration** – trajanje provjere autentičnosti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-277">**Duration** - How long the authentication took</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-278">**Endtime** – vrijeme završetka događaja provjere autentičnosti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-278">**Endtime** - When the authentication event ended</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-279">**Error** – šifra pogreške u slučaju da provjera autentičnosti nije uspjela</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-279">**Error** - Error code if the authentication failed</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-280">**Errordescription** – kratak opis pogreške</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-280">**Errordescription** - Brief description of the error</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-281">**Errorsource** – je li pogreška potekla iz servisa, biblioteke za provjeru autentičnosti ili aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-281">**Errorsource** - Did the error come from service, authentication library, or application</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-282">**Identityservice** – označava je li pozvan račun za Microsoftove servise (MSA) ili servis Azure Active Directory (AAD)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-282">**Identityservice** - Was Microsoft Service Account (MSA) or Azure Active Directory (AAD) service invoked</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-283">**Interactiveauthcontainer** – označava koja je vrsta upita prikazana</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-283">**Interactiveauthcontainer** - What type of prompt was shown</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-284">**Issilent** – označava je li prikazan upit</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-284">**Issilent** - Was a prompt shown</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-285">**Microsoft**\_**ADAL**\_**adal**\_**version** – verzija biblioteke Azure Active Directory Authentication Library (ADAL)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-285">**Microsoft**\_**ADAL**\_**adal**\_**version** - Version of the Azure Active Directory Authentication Library (ADAL)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-286">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_api\_error\_code** – šifra pogreške koju je biblioteka za provjeru autentičnosti poslala za ovaj pokušaj provjere autentičnosti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-286">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_api\_error\_code** - Error code emitted by authentication library for this authentication attempt</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-287">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_api\_id** – API koji je pozvan za taj pokušaj provjere autentičnosti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-287">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_api\_id** - API invoked for this authentication attempt</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-288">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_authority** – URL izdavatelja certifikata za Azure Active Directory koji je odgovoran za provjeru autentičnosti korisnika</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-288">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_authority** – Azure Active Directory authority URL responsible for authenticating the user</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-289">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_authority\_type** – potrošački / Microsoftov ugovor o usluzi (MSA) ili organizacijski / Azure Active Directory (AAD); trenutno uvijek AAD</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-289">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_authority\_type** – Consumer / Microsoft Service Agreement (MSA) vs organizational / Azure Active Directory (AAD); currently always AAD</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-290">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_authority\_validation\_status** – označava je li provjera autentičnosti provedena na strani servisa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-290">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_authority\_validation\_status** – Tells whether authentication completed on the service-side</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-291">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_broker\_app** – označava je li ADAL korišten kao posrednik za provjeru autentičnosti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-291">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_broker\_app** - Tells whether ADAL used a broker for authentication</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-292">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_broker\_app\_used** – označava naziv posrednika (npr. Windows Account Management)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-292">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_broker\_app\_used** – Tells the name of the broker (e.g., Windows Account Management)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-293">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_broker\_version** – označava verziju posrednika ako se koristi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-293">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_broker\_version** - Tells the version of the broker if used</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-294">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_event\_count** – broj događaja predmemoriranja koje je ADAL proveo tijekom dohvaćanja tokena</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-294">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_event\_count** - Number of cache events ADAL performed while retrieving token</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-295">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_event\_count\_max** – ako je signal skupni, označava maksimalni broj događaja predmemoriranja za bilo koji skupni događaj.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-295">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_event\_count\_max** - If this signal is aggregated, max cache events of any one of the aggregated events.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-296">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_event\_count\_min** – ako je signal skupni, označava minimalni broj događaja predmemoriranja za bilo koji skupni događaj.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-296">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_event\_count\_min** - If this signal is aggregated, min cache events of any one of the aggregated events.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-297">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_event\_count\_sum** – ako signal skupni, označava zbroj događaja predmemoriranja za sve skupne događaje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-297">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_event\_count\_sum** - If this signal is aggregated, sum of the cache events of all the aggregated events.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-298">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_read\_count** – označava koliko je puta API čitao iz predmemorije diska.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-298">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_read\_count** - How many times the API read from the disk cache.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-299">Postoji ako je došlo barem do jednog čitanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-299">Present if there was at least one read.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-300">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_read\_error\_count** – predstavlja broje neuspješnih čitanja iz predmemorije diska.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-300">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_read\_error\_count** - How many times the disk cache read failed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-301">Ako postoji, znači da čitanje barem jednom nije uspjelo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-301">Is present if there was at least one failure.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-302">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_read\_last\_error** – šifra pogreške ADAL-a.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-302">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_read\_last\_error** - ADAL error code.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-303">Postoji ako čitanje barem jednom nije uspjelo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-303">Present if there was at least one read failure.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-304">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_read\_last\_system\_error** – šifra sistemske pogreške.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-304">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_read\_last\_system\_error** - System error code.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-305">Postoji ako čitanje barem jednom nije uspjelo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-305">Is present if there was at least one read failure.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-306">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_write\_count** – označava koliko je puta API pisao u predmemoriju diska.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-306">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_write\_count** - How many times the API wrote to the disk cache.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-307">Postoji ako je došlo barem do jednog pisanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-307">Present if there was at least one write.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-308">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_write\_error\_count** – predstavlja broje neuspješnih pisanja u predmemoriju diska.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-308">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_write\_error\_count** - How many times the disk cache-write failed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-309">Postoji ako pisanje barem jednom nije uspjelo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-309">Present if there was at least one failure.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-310">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_write\_last\_error** – šifra pogreške ADAL-a.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-310">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_write\_last\_error** - ADAL error code.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-311">Postoji ako čitanje barem jednom nije uspjelo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-311">Present if there was at least one write failure.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-312">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_write\_last\_system\_error** – šifra sistemske pogreške.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-312">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_write\_last\_system\_error** - System error code.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-313">Postoji ako čitanje barem jednom nije uspjelo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-313">Present if there was at least one write failure.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-314">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_client\_id** – raspršeni ID aplikacije AAD</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-314">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_client\_id** - Hashed AAD app ID</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-315">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_extended\_expires\_on\_setting** – vrijednost true/false koja označava ima li token produljen životni vijek.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-315">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_extended\_expires\_on\_setting** - True/false telling if the token has an extended lifetime.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-316">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_http\_event\_coun**t – broj HTTP poziva koje je uputio ADAL.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-316">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_http\_event\_coun**t - Count of HTTP calls made by ADAL.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-317">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_http\_event\_count\_max** – ako je signal skupni, označava maksimalni broj HTTP poziva koje je ADAL uputio za bilo koji skupni događaj.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-317">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_http\_event\_count\_max** - If this signal is aggregated, max HTTP calls made by ADAL of any aggregated event.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-318">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_http\_event\_count\_min** – ako je signal skupni, označava minimalni broj HTTP poziva koje je ADAL uputio za bilo koji skupni događaj.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-318">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_http\_event\_count\_min** - If this signal is aggregated, min HTTP calls made by ADAL of any aggregated event.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-319">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_http\_event\_count\_sum** – ako je signal skupni, označava zbroj HTTP poziva koje je ADAL uputio za sve skupne događaje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-319">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_http\_event\_count\_sum** - If this signal is aggregated, sum of the HTTP calls made by ADAL of all the aggregated events.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-320">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_is\_silent\_ui** – vrijednost true/false koja označava je li ADAL prikazao korisničko sučelje (upit).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-320">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_is\_silent\_ui** - True/false telling if UI was shown (prompt) by ADAL.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-321">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_is\_successful** – vrijednost true/false koja označava je li API ADAL-a uspio.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-321">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_is\_successful** - True/false telling if ADAL API succeeded.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-322">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_logging\_pii\_enabled** – vrijednost true/false koja označava je li omogućen način rada za potpuno zapisivanje za ADAL.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-322">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_logging\_pii\_enabled** - True/false telling if ADAL full logging mode is enabled.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-323">Ti se podaci bilježe samo lokalno i ne šalju se u telemetriju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-323">This data is only logged locally, not emitted in telemetry.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-324">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_oauth\_error\_code** – šifra pogreške protokola OAuth koju je vratio servis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-324">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_oauth\_error\_code** – OAuth protocol error code returned by the service.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-325">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_prompt\_behavior** – prijava ili parametar koji nije HTTP proslijeđen servisu kojim se određuje može li se prikazati korisničko sučelje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-325">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_prompt\_behavior** - log-in or none HTTP parameter passed to service to specify if user interface can be shown.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-326">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_request\_id** – transakcijski GUID za zahtjev koji je ADAL poslao servisu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-326">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_request\_id** - Transactional GUID for the request emitted by ADAL to the service.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-327">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_response\_code** – šifra HTTP odgovora servisa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-327">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_response\_code** - HTTP response code from the service.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-328">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_response\_time** – vrijeme koje je bilo potrebno servisu da odgovori ADAL-u.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-328">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_response\_time** - How long it took service to return to ADAL.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-329">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_response\_time\_max** – ako je signal skupni, maksimalno vrijeme koje je ADAL-u bilo potrebno da se vrati iz API-ja u bilo kojem od skupnih događaja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-329">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_response\_time\_max** - If the signal is aggregated, the max time it took ADAL to return from its API among any of the aggregated events.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-330">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_response\_time\_min** – ako je signal skupni, minimalno vrijeme koje je servisu bilo potrebno da odgovori ADAL-u u bilo kojem od skupnih događaja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-330">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_response\_time\_min** - If the signal is aggregated, the min time it took the service to respond to ADAL among any of the aggregated events.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-331">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_response\_time\_sum** – ako je signal skupni, zbroj vremena koje je ADAL-u bilo potrebno da se vrati iz API-ja za sve skupne događaje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-331">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_response\_time\_sum** - If the signal is aggregated, the sum of the time it took ADAL to return from its API among all aggregated events.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-332">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_rt\_age** – starost tokena za osvježivanje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-332">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_rt\_age** – Age of the refresh token</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-338">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_telemetry\_pii\_enabled** – vrijednost true/false koja označava je li omogućen način rada za potpunu telemetriju za ADAL.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-338">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_telemetry\_pii\_enabled** - True/false telling if ADAL full telemetry mode is enabled.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-339">Naziv je pogrešan jer se ne šalje PII/EUII.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-339">The name is a misnomer, as no PII/EUII is emitted.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-340">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_tenant\_id** – GUID koji označava klijent kojem korisnik provjerene autentičnosti pripada.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-340">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_tenant\_id** - GUID identifying the tenant that the authenticated user belongs to.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-341">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_token\_acquisition\_from\_context** – opisuje ponašanje ADAL-a ovisno o tokenima u kontekstu provjere autentičnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-341">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_token\_acquisition\_from\_context** - Describes the ADAL behavior based on the tokens in the authentication context.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-342">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_token\_type** – token za osvježivanje (RT) ili token za osvježivanje više resursa (MRRT).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-342">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_token\_type** – Either refresh token (RT) or multi-resource refresh token (MRRT).</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-347">**Platform** – Win32/WinRT/Android/iOS/Mac</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-347">**Platform** - Win32/WinRT/Android/iOS/Mac</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-348">**Scenarioid** – GUID.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-348">**Scenarioid** – GUID.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-349">U jednom scenariju može biti veći broj događaja, npr. scenarijem se može dodavati novi račun, ali se u sklopu njega prikazuje više upita.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-349">Multiple events may belong to a single scenario, e.g. the scenario may be adding a new account but there are multiple prompts that occur as part of that scenario.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-350">Taj ID omogućuje korelaciju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-350">This ID enables correlation to happen.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-351">**Sessionid** – GUID koji određuje sesiju pokretanja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-351">**Sessionid** - GUID identifying the boot session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-353">**StartTime** – vrijeme pozivanja MATS API-ja Start\*Action</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-353">**Starttime** - Time at which the Start\*Action MATS API was called</span></span>

### <a name="officematsoneauthactionmicrosoftofficewin32"></a><span data-ttu-id="72c2f-359">Office.MATS.OneAuth.ActionMicrosoftOfficeWin32</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-359">Office.MATS.OneAuth.ActionMicrosoftOfficeWin32</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-360">Microsoft Auth Telemetry System (MATS) prikuplja se kada Office pokuša dohvatiti token za provjeru autentičnosti, bilo u pozadini ili putem upita korisniku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-360">Microsoft Auth Telemetry System (MATS) is collected when Office attempts to acquire an authentication token, either silently or through prompting.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-361">Kada pokušaj dohvaćanja ne uspije, uvrštavaju se informacije o pogrešci.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-361">When acquisition attempts fail, error information is included.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-362">Korisnici pomoću tih događaja mogu izbjeći prelazak u stanje neispravne provjere autentičnosti tako što:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-362">These events help our users avoid entering broken authentication states by:</span></span>

1) <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-363">će utvrditi mogu li klijenti uspješno dohvatiti token za provjeru autentičnosti sa servisa ili su prešli u stanje neispravne provjere autentičnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-363">Identifying whether clients can successfully obtain an authentication token from the service, or have entered a broken authentication state.</span></span>

2) <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-364">će procijeniti uzrokuju li promjene u klijentu ili servisu kritično nazadovanje sučelja i pouzdanosti provjere autentičnosti korisnika</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-364">Evaluate when changes occur on the client or services, whether they result in critical regressions in the user's authentication experience and reliability</span></span>

3) <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-365">u slučaju pogrešaka ti signali šalju važne šifre pogrešaka iz odgovorne komponente (koda klijentskog programa sustava Office, biblioteka za provjeru autentičnosti ili servisa izdavatelja certifikata) koje se mogu koristiti za klasifikaciju hitnosti, dijagnozu i otklanjanje problema</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-365">When failures occur, these signals emit important failure codes from the responsible component (Office client code, authentication libraries, or authority services) which can be used for triage, diagnosis and mitigation</span></span>

4) <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-366">signali služe kao podaci za razne nadzornike spremnosti za isporuku i stanja koji aktiviraju upozorenja da bi se naši inženjeri mogli brzo angažirati i skratiti vrijeme za otklanjanje kritičnih pogrešaka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-366">These signals power various ship readiness and health monitors which fire alerts so our engineers can engage quickly and reduce the time to mitigation of critical failures.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-367">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-367">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-368">**Accounttype** – vrsta računa koji se koristi za taj događaj provjere autentičnosti, na primjer, potrošački ili organizacijski.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-368">**Accounttype** - Type of the account used for this authentication event, for example, consumer or organizational.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-369">**ActionName** – neslužbeni naziv za taj događaj, ako je naveden.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-369">**Actionname** - Friendly name for this event, if one was provided.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-370">**Actiontype** – određuje vrstu upotrebljavane biblioteke za provjeru autentičnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-370">**Actiontype** - Specifies the type of authentication library in use.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-371">**Appaudience** – označava je li međuverzija aplikacije za internu ili vanjsku upotrebu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-371">**Appaudience** - Is the app build for internal or external use</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-372">**Appforcedprompt** – označava je li aplikacija nadjačala predmemoriju i prisilno prikazala upit</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-372">**Appforcedprompt** - Did the app override cache and force a prompt to be shown</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-373">**Appname** – naziv aplikacije koja provodi provjeru autentičnosti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-373">**Appname** - Name of the application doing authentication</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-374">**Appver** – verzija aplikacije koja provodi provjeru autentičnosti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-374">**Appver** - Version of the application doing authentication</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-375">**Askedforcreds** – označava je li aplikacija od korisnika tražila unos vjerodajnica za tu radnju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-375">**Askedforcreds** - Did the application ask the user to enter credentials for this action</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-376">**Authoutcome** – označava uspjeh, neuspjeh ili otkazivanje provjere autentičnosti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-376">**Authoutcome** - Did the authentication attempt succeed, fail, or was canceled</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-377">**Blockingprompt** – označava je li aplikacija izbacila upit na koji korisnik mora reagirati</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-377">**Blockingprompt** -  Did the application throw a prompt requiring user interaction</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-378">**Correlationid** – identifikator koji se upotrebljava za spajanje podataka o ovom pojedinačnom događaju sa servisnim podacima</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-378">**Correlationid** - Identifier used to join information regarding this individual event with services data</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-379">**Count** – ukupan broj skupnih radnji prijavljenih u ovom jednom događaju podataka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-379">**Count** - The total number of aggregated actions reported in this one data event.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-380">**Devicenetworkstate** – označava je li uređaj povezan s internetom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-380">**Devicenetworkstate** - Is the device connected to the internet.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-381">**Deviceprofiletelemetryid** – anonimni ID uređaja koji se koristi za mjerenje iskustva autentičnosti i pouzdanosti uređaja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-381">**Deviceprofiletelemetryid** - Anonymous device ID used to measure device-wide authentication experience and reliability.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-382">**Duration** – trajanje provjere autentičnosti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-382">**Duration** - How long the authentication took</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-383">**duration_max** – maksimalno trajanje bilo kojeg od skupnih događaja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-383">**duration_max** - Max duration of any one of the aggregated events</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-384">**duration_min** – min trajanje bilo kojeg od skupnih događaja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-384">**duration_min** - Min duration of any one of the aggregated events</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-385">**duration_sum** – zbroj trajanja svih skupnih događaja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-385">**duration_sum** - Sum of the duration of all the aggregated events</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-386">**endtime** – vrijeme završetka događaja provjere autentičnosti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-386">**endtime** - When the authentication event ended</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-387">**error** – šifra pogreške u slučaju da provjera autentičnosti nije uspjela</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-387">**error** - Error code if the authentication failed</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-388">**errordescription** – kratak opis pogreške</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-388">**errordescription** - Brief description of the error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-389">**errorsource** – je li pogreška potekla iz servisa, biblioteke za provjeru autentičnosti ili aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-389">**errorsource** - Did the error come from service, authentication library, or application</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-390">**eventtype** – izvještava li ovaj događaja o podatkovnoj točki provjere autentičnosti ili događaju pogreške kvalitete podataka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-390">**eventtype** - Is this event reporting an authentication datapoint, or a data quality error event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-391">Koristi se za mjerenje kvalitete podataka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-391">Used to measure data quality.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-392">**from_cache** – Booleov izraz koji predstavlja je li zapis iz predmemorije jezgre WAM-a ili dodatak</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-392">**from_cache** - Boolean representing whether the record is from the WAM core cache, or the plugin</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-393">**hasadaltelemetrija** – upućuje na to je li u knjižnici za provjeru autentičnosti servisa Azure Active Directory dostupna telemetrija za taj događaj.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-393">**hasadaltelemetry** - Indicates whether the Azure Active Directory Authentication Library (ADAL) provided telemetry for this event.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-394">**Identityservice** – označava je li pozvan račun za Microsoftove servise (MSA) ili servis Azure Active Directory (AAD)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-394">**Identityservice** - Was Microsoft Service Account (MSA) or Azure Active Directory (AAD) service invoked</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-395">**Interactiveauthcontainer** – označava koja je vrsta upita prikazana</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-395">**Interactiveauthcontainer** - What type of prompt was shown</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-396">**Issilent** – označava je li prikazan upit ili je to bio tihi (pozadinski) događaj provjere autentičnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-396">**Issilent** - Was a prompt shown or was this a silent (background) authentication event.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-397">**Microsoft_ADAL_adal_version** – verzija biblioteke Azure Active Directory Authentication Library (ADAL)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-397">**Microsoft_ADAL_adal_version** - Version of the Azure Active Directory Authentication Library (ADAL)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-398">**Microsoft_ADAL_api_error_code** – šifra pogreške koju je biblioteka za provjeru autentičnosti poslala za ovaj pokušaj provjere autentičnosti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-398">**Microsoft_ADAL_api_error_code** - Error code emitted by authentication library for this authentication attempt</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-399">**Microsoft_ADAL_api_id** – API koji je pozvan za taj pokušaj provjere autentičnosti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-399">**Microsoft_ADAL_api_id** - API invoked for this authentication attempt</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-400">**Microsoft_ADAL_application_name** – naziv aplikacije/procesa koji koristi ADAL.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-400">**Microsoft_ADAL_application_name** - The name of the application / process using ADAL.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-401">**Microsoft_ADAL_application_version** – verzija aplikacije koja koristi ADAL.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-401">**Microsoft_ADAL_application_version** - The version of the application using ADAL.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-402">**Microsoft_ADAL_authority** – URL izdavatelja certifikata za Azure Active Directory koji je odgovoran za provjeru autentičnosti korisnika</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-402">**Microsoft_ADAL_authority** - Azure Active Directory authority URL responsible for authenticating the user</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-403">**Microsoft_ADAL_authority_type** – potrošački / Microsoftov ugovor o usluzi (MSA) ili organizacijski / Azure Active Directory (AAD); trenutačno uvijek AAD</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-403">**Microsoft_ADAL_authority_type** - Consumer / Microsoft Service Agreement (MSA) vs organizational / Azure Active Directory (AAD); currently always AAD</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-404">**Microsoft_ADAL_authority_validation_status**– označava je li provjera autentičnosti provedena na strani servisa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-404">**Microsoft_ADAL_authority_validation_status** - Tells whether authentication completed on the service-side</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-405">**Microsoft_ADAL_broker_app** – označava je li ADAL korišten kao posrednik za provjeru autentičnosti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-405">**Microsoft_ADAL_broker_app** - Tells whether ADAL used a broker for authentication</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-406">**Microsoft_ADAL_broker_app_used** – označava naziv posrednika (npr. Windows Account Management)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-406">**Microsoft_ADAL_broker_app_used** - Tells the name of the broker (e.g., Windows Account Management)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-550">**WAM_oauth_error_code** – sadrži šifru pogreške koji je servis vratio kao dio protokola oauth.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-550">**WAM_oauth_error_code** - Contains the error code returned by the service as part of the oauth protocol.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-551">**WAM_prompt_behavior** – određuje je li ovaj upit zatražila aplikacija, ili, može li ovaj zahtjev preskočiti pitanja ako može neprimjetno provjeriti autentičnost.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-551">**WAM_prompt_behavior** - Specifies if this prompt is forced by the app, or, if this request might skip prompting if it can silently authenticate.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-552">**WAM_provider_id** – Određuje Microsoftovu krajnju točku za ustanovu koja se koristi za scenarij provjere autentičnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-552">**WAM_provider_id** - Specifies the Microsoft endpoint for the authority in use for the auth scenario.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-553">**WAM_redirect_uri** – URI za preusmjeravanje registriran za aplikaciju u servisu Azure Active Directory.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-553">**WAM_redirect_uri** - The redirect URI registered for the application in Azure Active Directory.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-554">**WAM_resource** – označava resurs za koji se traži token.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-554">**WAM_resource**  - The resource for which a token is requested for.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-555">**WAM_server_error_code** – šifra pogreške koju je servis vratio u WAM.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-555">**WAM_server_error_code** - The error code returned by the service to WAM.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-556">**WAM_server_sub_code** – dodatna šifra pogreške koja se upotrebljava za daljnje razbijanje uzroka kvara koji je vratio servis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-556">**WAM_server_sub_code** - An additional error code used to further break down the causes for failure, returned by the service.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-557">**WAM_silent_code** – šifra pogreške koja je naišla na tihi interni pokušaj WAM-a, prije nego što pošalje upit korisniku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-557">**WAM_silent_code** - The error code encountered by the internal silent attempt WAM makes, prior to prompting the user.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-558">**WAM_silent_mats** – označava neiskorišteno.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-558">**WAM_silent_mats** - Unused.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-559">**WAM_silent_message** – označava poruku o pogrešci povezanu sa unutarnjim tihim pokušajima WAM-a, prije nego što pošalje upit korisniku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-559">**WAM_silent_message** - The error message associated with the internal silent attempt WAM makes, prior to prompting the user.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-560">**WAM_silent_status** – označava status uspjeha/neuspjeha za tihi interni pokušaj WAM-a, prije nego što pošalje upit korisniku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-560">**WAM_silent_status** - The success/fail status for the internal silent attempt WAM makes, prior to prompting the user.</span></span>
