- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-562">**WAM_ui_visible** – prisutno ako je korisniku prikazan najmanje jedan prozor korisničkog sučelja, bilo ‘true’ ili ‘false’</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-562">**WAM_ui_visible** - Present if at least one UI window was shown to the user, either ‘true’ or ‘false’</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-563">**WAM_x_ms_clitelem** – prisutno ako servis vrati zaglavlje “x-ms-clitelem"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-563">**WAM_x_ms_clitelem** - Present if service returns header “x-ms-clitelem"</span></span>


### <a name="officematsoneauthtransactionmicrosoftofficewin32"></a><span data-ttu-id="72c2f-564">Office.MATS.OneAuth.TransactionMicrosoftOfficeWin32</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-564">Office.MATS.OneAuth.TransactionMicrosoftOfficeWin32</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-565">Microsoft Auth Telemetry System (MATS) prikuplja se kada Office pokuša dohvatiti token za provjeru autentičnosti, bilo u pozadini ili putem upita korisniku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-565">Microsoft Auth Telemetry System (MATS) is collected when Office attempts to acquire an authentication token, either silently or through prompting.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-566">Ovaj je događaj nadređen jednom ili više ActionMicrosoftOffice događaja, što omogućuje grupiranje povezanih događaja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-566">This event is a parent of one or more ActionMicrosoftOffice events, allowing related events to be grouped together.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-567">Korisnici pomoću tih događaja mogu izbjeći prelazak u stanje neispravne provjere autentičnosti tako što:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-567">These events help our users avoid entering broken authentication states by:</span></span>

1) <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-568">će utvrditi mogu li klijenti uspješno dohvatiti token za provjeru autentičnosti sa servisa ili su prešli u stanje neispravne provjere autentičnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-568">Identifying whether clients can successfully obtain an authentication token from the service, or have entered a broken authentication state.</span></span>

2) <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-569">će procijeniti uzrokuju li promjene u klijentu ili servisu kritično nazadovanje sučelja i pouzdanosti provjere autentičnosti korisnika</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-569">Evaluate when changes occur on the client or services, whether they result in critical regressions in the user's authentication experience and reliability</span></span>

3) <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-570">u slučaju pogrešaka ti signali šalju važne šifre pogrešaka iz odgovorne komponente (koda klijentskog programa sustava Office, biblioteka za provjeru autentičnosti ili servisa izdavatelja certifikata) koje se mogu koristiti za klasifikaciju hitnosti, dijagnozu i otklanjanje problema</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-570">When failures occur, these signals emit important failure codes from the responsible component (Office client code, authentication libraries, or authority services) which can be used for triage, diagnosis and mitigation</span></span>

4) <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-571">signali služe kao podaci za razne nadzornike spremnosti za isporuku i stanja koji aktiviraju upozorenja da bi se naši inženjeri mogli brzo angažirati i skratiti vrijeme za otklanjanje kritičnih pogrešaka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-571">These signals power various ship readiness and health monitors which fire alerts so our engineers can engage quickly and reduce the time to mitigation of critical failures.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-572">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-572">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-573">**Actiontype** – „oneauthtransaction" je jedina vrijednost.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-573">**Actiontype** - "oneauthtransaction" is the only value.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-574">**Appaudience** –označava ciljnu skupinu aplikacije (automatizacija, pred proizvodnja ili proizvodnja)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-574">**Appaudience** - Application audience (Automation, Preproduction or Production)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-575">**Appname** – označava naziv aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-575">**Appname** - App name</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-576">**Appver**– označava verziju aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-576">**Appver** - App version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-577">**Authoutcome** – označava uspjeh, neuspjeh ili otkazivanje provjere autentičnosti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-577">**Authoutcome** - Did the authentication attempt succeed, fail, or was canceled</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-578">**Correlationid** – identifikator koji se upotrebljava za spajanje podataka o ovom pojedinačnom događaju sa servisnim podacima</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-578">**Correlationid** - Identifier used to join information regarding this individual event with services data</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-579">**Count** – označava koliko je puta došlo do pogreške</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-579">**Count** - Number of times the error occurred</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-580">**Devicenetworkstate** – stanje mreže uređaja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-580">**Devicenetworkstate** - Device network state</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-581">**Deviceprofilatelemetryid** – ID telemetrije profila uređaja (niz kojim se koristi MATS za određivanje određenog uređaja)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-581">**Deviceprofiletelemetryid** - Device profile telemetry ID (string used by MATS to identify a specific device)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-582">**duration_max** – označava minimalno trajanje, u milisekundama, transakcija koje se skupljaju na tom signalu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-582">**duration_max** - Minimum duration, in milliseconds, of the transactions aggregated on this signal.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-583">**duration_min** – označava maksimalno trajanje, u milisekundama, transakcija koje se skupljaju na tom signalu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-583">**duration_min** - Maximum duration, in milliseconds, of the transactions aggregated on this signal.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-584">**duration_sum** – označava zbroj trajanja transakcija koje se skupljaju na tom signalu u milisekundama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-584">**duration_sum** - Sum of durations, in milliseconds, of the transactions aggregated on this signal.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-585">**Endtime** – označava vrijeme u kojem je završila transakcija OneAuth.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-585">**Endtime** - Time at which the OneAuth transaction ended.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-586">**Error** – OneAuth kôd statusa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-586">**Error** - OneAuth status code.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-587">**Eventtype** – označava vrstu događaja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-587">**Eventtype** - Event type</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-588">**Issilent** – False ako je prikazano korisničko sučelje; true ako je riječ o događaju u pozadini.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-588">**Issilent** - False if UI was shown; true if it was a background event.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-589">**oneauth_api** – određuje javni API za OneAuth koji je pozvan.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-589">**oneauth_api** - Specifies the public API of OneAuth that was invoked.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-590">**oneauth_Domain** – ako je poziv API-ja uzrokovao pogrešku, to je sistemska domena te pogreške.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-590">**oneauth_Domain** - If the API call resulted in an error, this is the system domain of that error.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-591">**oneauth_ErrorCode** – šifra pogreške koja predstavlja interno stanje pogreške za OneAuth.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-591">**oneauth_ErrorCode** - Error code representing the internal error state for OneAuth.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-592">Zamjenjuje staro polje oneauth_errortag field.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-592">Replaces the old oneauth_errortag field.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-593">**oneauth_errortag** – numerički identifikator za redak kôda koji je odgovoran za generiranje pogreške.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-593">**oneauth_errortag** - Numerical identifier for a line of code that was responsible for generating an error.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-594">**oneauth_ExecutionFlow** – niz oznaka koje identificiraju put koda koji je preuzeo ovaj API.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-594">**oneauth_ExecutionFlow** - A series of tags identifying the codepath this API invocation took.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-595">**oneauth_internalerror** – šifra pogreške koja predstavlja interno stanje pogreške za OneAuth.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-595">**oneauth_internalerror** - Error code representing the internal error state for OneAuth.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-596">**oneauth_ServerErrorCode** – pogreška poslužitelja vraćena u OneAuth po završetku tog poziva API-ja, ako se naiđe na nju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-596">**oneauth_ServerErrorCode** - The server error returned to OneAuth at the conclusion of this API call, if one was encountered.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-597">**oneauth_SystemErrorCode** – sistemska pogreška vraćena u OneAuth po završetku tog poziva API-ja, ako se naiđe na nju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-597">**oneauth_SystemErrorCode** - The system error returned to OneAuth at the conclusion of this API call, if one was encountered.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-598">**oneauth_Tag** – oznaka OneAuth koja označava konačno mjesto u kodu postignuto na kraju ovog poziva API-ja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-598">**oneauth_Tag** - The OneAuth tag designating the final place in code reached at the conclusion of this API call.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-599">**oneauth_transactionuploadid** – određuje nasumično generirani interni GUID koji se preslikava na određeno pozivanje OneAuth API-ja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-599">**oneauth_transactionuploadid** - Specifies the randomly-generated internal GUID that maps to the specific invocation of a OneAuth API.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-600">**oneauth_version** – verzija SDK-a za OneAuth.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-600">**oneauth_version** - The version of the OneAuth SDK.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-601">**Platform** – OS (0: Win32; 1: Android; 2: iOS; 3: MacOS; 4: WinRT</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-601">**Platform** - OS Platform (0: Win32, 1: Android, 2: iOS, 3: MacOS, 4: WinRT</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-602">**Scenarioname** – naziv scenarija za koji je potrebna provjera autentičnosti, a određuje ga aplikacija za pozivanje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-602">**Scenarioname** - Name of the scenario for which auth is necessary, specified by the calling application.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-603">**Schemaver**– označava verziju sheme</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-603">**Schemaver** - Schema Version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-604">**Sdkver** – označava verziju SDK-a MATS-a</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-604">**Sdkver** - Version of the MATS sdk</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-605">**Sessionid** – označava ID sesije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-605">**Sessionid** - Session ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-606">**severityError** – označava ozbiljnost</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-606">**severityError** - severity</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-607">**startime** – označava vrijeme u kojem je započela transakcija OneAuth.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-607">**starttime** - Time at which the OneAuth transaction began.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-608">**Timestamp** – označava vremensku oznaku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-608">**Timestamp** - Timestamp</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-609">**Type** – označava vrstu pogreške</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-609">**Type** - Error type</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-610">**Uploaded** – Jedinstveni identifikator za ovaj određeni događaj, u svrhe uklanjanja duplikata.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-610">**Uploaded** - Unique identifier for this particular event, for de-duping purposes.</span></span>


### <a name="onenotesigninssoexternalappsaccountfound"></a><span data-ttu-id="72c2f-611">OneNote.SignIn.SSOExternalAppsAccountFound</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-611">OneNote.SignIn.SSOExternalAppsAccountFound</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-612">Ovaj se događaj bilježi kada se na popisu računa koje nudi TokenSharingManager pronađe račun s valjanim tokenom osvježavanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-612">This event is logged when an account with a valid refresh token is found among the list of accounts provided by TokenSharingManager.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-613">Taj je scenarij specifičan za jedinstvenu prijavu (SSO).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-613">This scenario is specific to Single Sign-on (SSO).</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-614">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-614">The following fields are collected:</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-615">**AccountType** - Bilježi vrstu računa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-615">**AccountType** - Logs the type of account</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-616">**ProviderPackageID**-zapisuje ID paketa aplikacije koja je dala taj račun</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-616">**ProviderPackageID** - Logs the package ID of the app that provided this account</span></span>

### <a name="onenotesigninssoexternalappsinvalidaccount"></a><span data-ttu-id="72c2f-617">OneNote.SignIn.SSOExternalAppsInvalidAccount</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-617">OneNote.SignIn.SSOExternalAppsInvalidAccount</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-618">Taj se događaj bilježi kada se prilikom pokušaja dohvaćanja tokena osvježavanja za račun na popisu računa koje nudi TokenSharingManager dogodi pogreška.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-618">This event is logged when there was an error when attempting to obtain a refresh token for an account in the list of accounts provided by TokenSharingManager.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-619">Taj je scenarij specifičan za jedinstvenu prijavu (SSO)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-619">This scenario is specific to Single Sign-on (SSO)</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-620">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-620">The following fields are collected:</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-621">**RawError** - zapisuje pogrešku RAW dobivenu prilikom pokušaja dohvaćati tokena osvježavanja pomoću danog računa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-621">**RawError** - Logs the raw error obtained when attempting to get a refresh token with the given account</span></span>

### <a name="onenotestickynotesfetchtokencompleted"></a><span data-ttu-id="72c2f-622">OneNote.StickyNotes.FetchTokenCompleted</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-622">OneNote.StickyNotes.FetchTokenCompleted</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-623">Ovaj je događaj zapisan nakon provjere autentičnosti, po dovršetku dohvaćanja tokena osvježavanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-623">This event is logged post authentication, once fetching of refresh token is completed.</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-624">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-624">The following fields are collected:</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-625">**ErrorMessage** - ako dohvaćanje tokena nije uspjelo, to bi zabilježilo poruku o pogrešci</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-625">**ErrorMessage** - If fetching of token failed, this would log the error message</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-626">**Result** - zapisuje rezultat pokušaja dohvaćanja tokena</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-626">**Result** - Logs the result of token fetching attempt</span></span>

Microsoft 365 Apps za velike tvrtke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-641">**Data\_ProductReleaseId** - Product we're installing, i.e. Microsoft 365 Apps for enterprise</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-651">**Data\_CompressionLevel –** način kompresije datoteka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-651">**Data\_CompressionLevel -** how the files are compressed</span></span>

### <a name="officeclicktorunrepomanlogger"></a><span data-ttu-id="72c2f-713">Office.ClickToRun.RepomanLogger</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-713">Office.ClickToRun.RepomanLogger</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-714">Izvještava o statusu za novi kanal ažuriranja „klikom do cilja“ („Repoman“) i ako uspješno preuzima i primjenjuje ažuriranja za Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-714">Reports on the status for the new Click-to-Run update pipeline ("Repoman") and if it successfully downloads and applies Office updates.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-715">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-715">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-716">**ApplySucceeded –** Vrijednost true ako je kanal uspješno primijenio ažuriranje sustava Office, vrijednost false ako nije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-716">**ApplySucceeded -** True if the pipeline successfully applied an Office update, false if not.</span></span>
  
  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-717">**DownloadSucceeded –** Vrijednost true ako je kanal uspješno preuzeo ažuriranje sustava Office, vrijednost false ako nije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-717">**DownloadSucceeded -** True if the pipeline successfully downloaded an Office update, false if not.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-718">**ErrorCode –** Kôd posljednje pogreške koja se dogodila u kanalu „klikom do cilja“ Repoman.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-718">**ErrorCode -** The code of the last error that occurred in the Click-to-Run Repoman pipeline.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-719">**ErrorDetails –**  Dodatni detalji posljednje pogreške koja se dogodila u kanalu „klikom do cilja“ Repoman.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-719">**ErrorDetails -**  Additional error details of the last error that occurred in the Click-to-Run Repoman pipeline.</span></span>
 
  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-720">**ErrorMessage –** Poruka posljednje pogreške koja se dogodila u kanalu „klikom do cilja“ Repoman.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-720">**ErrorMessage -** The message of the last error that occurred in the Click-to-Run Repoman pipeline.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-721">**OpenStreamSessionSucceeded –** Vrijednost true ako kanal uspješno stvara sesiju za strujanje ažuriranja sustava Office, vrijednost false ako ne stvara.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-721">**OpenStreamSessionSucceeded -** True if the pipeline successfully creates a session for streaming an Office update, false if not.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-722">**RepomanErrorMessage –** Poruka o pogrešci primljena od sustava  repoman.dll.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-722">**RepomanErrorMessage -** The error message received from the repoman.dll.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1768">**Origin –**    vrijednost niza koja govori koji od podržanih izvora (Portoriko [PR], Singapur [SG], Dublin [DB]) treba upotrijebiti za početno instalacijsko strujanje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1768">**Origin –**    String value telling us which of the supported origins (Puerto Rico [PR], Singapore [SG], Dublin [DB]) should be used for initial installation streaming</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1769">**PlatformFromLink –**    Niz koji pokazuje traženi x86 | x64 | zadani bit sustava Office zatražen od C2R servisa postavljanja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1769">**PlatformFromLink –**    String indicating the requested x86|x64|default bitness of Office requested from the C2R Setup service</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1770">**PlatformOfExistingInstallation –**    niz koji pokazuje je li x86 ili X64 Office već instaliran na uređaju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1770">**PlatformOfExistingInstallation –**    String indicating whether x86 vs. X64 Office was already installed on the device</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1771">**PlatformToInstall –**    niz koji pokazuje konačnu odluku o tome treba li instalirati x86 ili X64 Office</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1771">**PlatformToInstall –**    String indicating the final decision on whether x86 vs. X64 Office should be installed</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1772">**PRID –**    Vrijednost niza koja predstavlja traženi ID izdanja proizvoda u scenariju za instalaciju kod korisnika (primjerice, "O365ProPlusRetail")</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1772">**PRID –**    String value representing the requested Product Release ID in a consumer installation scenario (for example, "O365ProPlusRetail")</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1773">**PridsToMigrateFromCentennial-** Niz proizvoda sustava Office za migraciju iz instalacija trgovine u značajku "klikom do cilja"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1773">**PridsToMigrateFromCentennial-** String of Office products to migrate from Store installations to Click-To-Run</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1774">**ProductsToAdd –**    serijalizirani niz koji upućuje C2R klijenta na kombinacije proizvoda/kulture koje bi trebao instalirati</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1774">**ProductsToAdd –**    The serialized string that instructs C2R Client on which Product/Culture combinations it should be installing</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1775">**ProductsToMigrateFromO15C2R-** Niz proizvoda i kultura sustava Office za migraciju iz instalacije sustava Office 2013 značajkom "klikom do cilja"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1775">**ProductsToMigrateFromO15C2R -** String of Office products and cultures to migrate from an Office 2013 Click-To-Run installation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1776">**ProductsToRemove –**    Serijalizirani niz koji upućuje C2R klijenta na kombinacije proizvoda/kulture koje bi trebao deinstalirati</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1776">**ProductsToRemove –**    The serialized string that instructs C2R Client on which Product/Culture combinations it should be uninstalling</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1777">**SharedComputerLicensing –**    Booleov izraz koji ukazuje na to je li IT administrator zatražio postavljanje da bi se omogućila značajka „SharedComputerLicensing”</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1777">**SharedComputerLicensing –**    Boolean indicating whether an IT Admin requested setup to enable the "SharedComputerLicensing" feature</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1778">**ShouldActivate –**    Booleov izraz koji ukazuje na to je li IT administrator zatražio automatski pokušaj aktiviranja licenciranja u datoteci configuration.xml</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1778">**ShouldActivate–**    Boolean indicating whether an IT Admin requested an automatic licensing activation attempt in their configuration.xml</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1779">**ShouldUninstallCentennial -** Booleova zastavica koja upućuje na to je li proizvode iz trgovine potrebno deinstalirati</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1779">**ShouldUninstallCentennial -** Boolean flag indicating whether Office products from the Store should be uninstalled</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1780">**VersionToInstall –**    vrijednost niza verzije sustava Office „16.0.xxxxx.yyyyy” koja se instalira</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1780">**VersionToInstall–**    String value of the Office "16.0.xxxxx.yyyyy" version that is being installed</span></span>

### <a name="officeclicktorununiversalbootstrapperexecute"></a><span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1781">Office.ClickToRun.UniversalBootstrapper.Execute</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1781">Office.ClickToRun.UniversalBootstrapper.Execute</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1782">Izvješćuje o poduzetim radnjama koje su utjecale na stroj, što je utvrđeno obrazloženim podacima iz opcije "CalculateParameters"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1782">Reports on the machine-impactful actions taken, as determined by the reasoned-over data from "CalculateParameters"</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1783">**AvailableClientVersionText –**    vrijednost niza C2R klijenta verzije „16.0.xxxxx.yyyyy” pronađena u verziji Deskriptor XML, koji se koristi kako bi se utvrdilo treba li ažurirati trenutno instalirani C2R klijent</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1783">**AvailableClientVersionText –**    String value of the C2R Client "16.0.xxxxx.yyyyy" version found in the Version Descriptor XML, which is used to determine whether a currently installed C2R Client should be updated</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1784">**CleanFireflyAction –**    „true” ako se planira pokretanje zadatka CleanFireFlyAction tijekom ove instalacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1784">**CleanFireflyAction –**    "true" if the CleanFireFlyAction task is scheduled to run during this installation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1785">**CleanO15Action –**    „true” ako se planira pokretanje zadatka CleanO15Action tijekom ove instalacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1785">**CleanO15Action –**    "true" if the CleanO15Action task is scheduled to run during this installation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1786">**CMDMode –**    neslužbeni niz koji odgovara ukupnoj zamjeni načina otkriven je u cmd argumentima koji su proslijeđeni u exe.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1786">**CMDMode –**    The friendly string corresponding to which overall mode switch was detected in the cmd arguments passed to the exe.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1787">Mogućnosti su: automatsko pokretanje, konfiguriranje, korisnik, preuzimanje, pomoć, program za pakiranje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1787">Possibilities are:  autorun, configure, consumer, download, help, packager</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1788">**DeliveryMechanism –**   „FFNRoot” guid izdvojen iz verzije Deskriptora XML (koju je izdao RDX), koji nam govori iz koje publike/kanala potječe izvor za izgradnju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1788">**DeliveryMechanism –**    The "FFNRoot" guid extracted from the Version Descriptor XML (stamped by RDX), which tells us which audience/channel the build source came from</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1789">**DownloadC2RClientAction –**    „true” ako se planira pokretanje zadatka DownloadC2RClientAction tijekom ove instalacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1789">**DownloadC2RClientAction –**    "true" if the DownloadC2RClientAction task is scheduled to run during this installation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1790">**ErrorCode –**    vrijednost cijelog broja povezana je s neobrađenom iznimkom</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1790">**ErrorCode –**    Integer value associated with an unhandled exception</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1791">**ErrorDetails –**    Niz koji opisuje mjesto na kojem se desila neobrađena iznimka (funkcija, datoteka, broj retka, dodatni parametri koje je postavio bacač)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1791">**ErrorDetails –**    String that describes the location of where an unhandled exception occurred (function, file, line number, additional parameters set by the thrower)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1792">**ErrorMessage –**    Niz definiran na mjestu izbacivanja neobrađene iznimke, opisujući prirodu neuspjeha</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1792">**ErrorMessage –**    String defined at the point where an unhandled exception was thrown, describing the nature of the failure</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1793">**ErrorType –**    niz koji opisuje kategoriju neobrađene iznimke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1793">**ErrorType –**    String describing the category of an unhandled exception</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1794">**ExitCode –**   Vrijednost cijelog broja  povezana s rezultatom pokretanja automatskog pokretanja, ukazuje na uspjeh nasuprot određenim vrstama neuspjeha</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1794">**ExitCode –**    Integer value associated with the result of running the Execute phase of the bootstrapper, indicating success vs. specific types of failure</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1795">**LaunchAction –**    "true" ako se planira pokretanje zadatka LaunchAction tijekom instalacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1795">**LaunchAction –**    "true" if the LaunchAction task is scheduled to run during this installation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1796">**LaunchUpdateAction –**    „true” ako se planira pokretanje zadatka LaunchUpdateAction tijekom instalacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1796">**LaunchUpdateAction –**    "true" if the LaunchUpdateAction task is scheduled to run during this installation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1797">**PreReqResult –**    Vrijednost cijelog broja identifikatora rezultata kada su izvedene provjere bez preduvjeta (prolaz/pad/ponovno pokretanje)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1797">**PreReqResult –**    The integer enum value of the result when PreReq checks were performed (pass/fail/re-run)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1798">**UnexpectedAction –**    "true" ako se planira pokretanje zadatka (slučaja pogreške) UnexpectedAction tijekom instalacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1798">**UnexpectedAction –**    "true" if the UnexpectedAction task (an error case) is scheduled to run during this installation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1799">**VersionToInstall –**   Vrijednost niza verzije sustava Office "16.0.xxxxx.yyyyy" koja se instalira</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1799">**VersionToInstall –**    String value of the Office "16.0.xxxxx.yyyyy" version that is being installed</span></span>

### <a name="officeserviceabilitymanagerinventoryaddonheartbeat"></a><span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1800">Office.ServiceabilityManager.InventoryAddon.Heartbeat</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1800">Office.ServiceabilityManager.InventoryAddon.Heartbeat</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1801">*[Ovaj je događaj uklonjen iz trenutačnih međuverzija sustava Office, ali se i dalje može pojavljivati u starijim međuverzijama.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1801">*[This event has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1802">Taj se događaj koristi za pribavljanje standardnih meta-podataka pri svakom pokretanju dodatka Inventar, koji je dio Upravitelja za Office servisiranje i koristi se za informacije o Office inventaru na onim strojevima koje je IT administrator uključio.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1802">This event is used to acquire standard metadata on each run of the Inventory add-on, which is part of the Office Serviceability Manager and is used for inventory Office information on those machines for which an IT admin has opted in.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1803">Meta-podatak od posebnog zanimanja u ovom slučaju je ID sesije, a koristi se za povezivanje s drugim podacima pohranjenima unutar usluge na oblaku po klijentu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1803">The metadata of specific interest here is the session ID, and it is used for linking to other data stored within a per-tenant cloud service.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1804">Ovaj događaj nema dodatnih polja jer su relevantni samo meta-podaci.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1804">This event contains no extra fields since only the metadata is relevant.</span></span>

### <a name="officeserviceabilitymanagerinventoryaddonresults"></a><span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1805">Office.ServiceabilityManager.InventoryAddon.Results</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1805">Office.ServiceabilityManager.InventoryAddon.Results</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1806">Taj se događaj bilježi kada se poziv na web-servis u sklopu dodatka "klikom do cilja" za inventar upravitelja za servis dovrši, neovisno o tome uspijeva li ili ne uspijeva.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1806">This event is logged when the call to the webservice made within the Click-to-Run Serviceability Manager Inventory add-on completes, irrespective of whether it succeeds or fails.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1807">To je u suštini posljednja operacija unutar dodatka za praćenje ukupnog stanja rada.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1807">This is essentially the last operation within the add-on to track the overall operation status.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1808">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1808">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1809">**ActionDetail** – dodatne pojedinosti u slučaju nastupanja kvara.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1809">**ActionDetail** -  Additional details for when a failure occurs.</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1810">Ako zahtjev HTTP-a uspije, ActionDetail bit će 0.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1810">If the HTTP request succeeds, ActionDetail will be 0.</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1811">Ako Polje rezultata nije U redu (tj. nije 0), što znači da zahtjev nije poslan, u ovom će se polju zabilježiti kod interne pogreške koji je jednak Polju rezultata.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1811">If the Result field is not OK (i.e. not 0), which means that the request is not sent, this field will log the internal error code which is the same as the Result field.</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1812">Ako je Polje rezultata U redu (tj. 0), što znači da je kôd odgovora HTTP-a >= 300, u njemu će se zabilježiti kôd odgovora HTTP-a (npr. 404).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1812">If the Result field is OK (i.e. 0), which means that the HTTP response code >= 300, it will log the HTTP response code (e.g. 404).</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1813">**Rezultat** – brojčana oznaka pogreške koju vraćaju API-jevi poziva web-servisa sustava Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1813">**Result** - Numeric error code flags returned by the Office webservice call APIs.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1814">– npr. 3 znači da postoji problem s inicijalizacijom zaglavlja HTTP-a.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1814">– e.g. 3 would mean that there was a problem initializing the HTTP headers.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1815">**Type** – dodatne informacije o vrsti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1815">**Type** - Additional type information.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1816">U slučaju Zaliha, ove informacije određuju vrstu tereta koji se šalje – npr. pune ili samo delta promjene.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1816">In the case of the Inventory, this information specifies the type of payload being sent – e.g. full or just a delta of changes.</span></span> 

-  <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1817">**WebCallSource** – vrijednost za numeriranje (koja se određuje kao cijeli broj) koja označava dodatak upravitelja servisa koji je bio izvor poziva:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1817">**WebCallSource** - An enumeration value (specified as an integer) indicating the Serviceability Manager add-on that was the source of the call:</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1818">Zalihe: 0</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1818">Inventory: 0</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1819">Konfiguriranje zaliha: 1</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1819">Inventory Configuration: 1</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1820">Pravilnik o zalihama: 2</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1820">Inventory Policy: 2</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1821">Stanje mreže zaliha: 3</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1821">Inventory Network Status: 3</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1822">Upravitelj servisa: 4</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1822">Serviceability Manager: 4</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1823">Mogućnost upravljanja: 5</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1823">Manageability: 5</span></span>

### <a name="officeserviceabilitymanagerwebservicefailure"></a><span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1824">Office.ServiceabilityManager.WebserviceFailure</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1824">Office.ServiceabilityManager.WebserviceFailure</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1825">Ova se naredba bilježi svaki put kad ne uspije poziv na web-servis unutar jednog od dodataka upravitelja servisa sustava Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1825">Whenever a call to a webservice within one of the Office Serviceability Manager add-ins fails, this statement is logged.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1826">Pogreške mogu nastati zbog unutarnjih pogrešaka ili nemogućnosti povezivanja s web-servisom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1826">Failures can be due to internal failures or an inability to connect to the webservice.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1827">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1827">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1828">**Add-on** - Programski dodatak upravitelja servisa "klikom do cilja" iz kojeg je pokrenut poziv na web-servis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1828">**Add-on** - The Click-to-Run Serviceability Manager add-on from which the webservice call was made.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1829">To može imati vrijednosti kao što su zalihe, upravljanje itd., kodirane kao numerička vrijednost.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1829">This can have values like inventory, manageability, etc. encoded as a numeric value.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1830">**Correlation ID** – nasumično generirani GUID specifičan za trenutnu instancu koji je poslan web-servisu kako bi povezao pozive između klijenta i poslužitelja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1830">**Correlation ID** - A randomly generated GUID specific to the current instance that is sent to the webservice to correlate calls between the client and the server.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1831">**ErrorInfo** - brojčana oznaka pogreške koju vraćaju API-jevi poziva web-servisa sustava Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1831">**ErrorInfo** - Numeric error code information returned by the Office webservice call APIs.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1832">**ErrorMessage** – poruka koja omogućuje daljnji uvid u pogrešku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1832">**ErrorMessage** - A message providing further insight into the failure.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1833">Svaka se vrsta greške mapira na niz ugrađen u kôd, a neke se vrste grešaka mapiraju na potencijalno više nizova ovisno o posebnoj vrsti greške.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1833">Each error type maps to a hardcoded string, with some error types mapping to potentially multiple strings depending on the specific nature of the failure.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1834">**Function** – funkcija u kodu iz koje je došlo do trenutnog poziva.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1834">**Function** - The function in the code from which the current call occurred.</span></span>

## <a name="enhanced-configuration-service-ecs-events"></a><span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1836">Događaji servisa za eksperimentiranje i konfiguraciju (ECS-a)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1836">Enhanced Configuration Service (ECS) events</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingactivationwizard"></a><span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1931">Office.Licensing.ActivationWizard</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1931">Office.Licensing.ActivationWizard</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingfullvalidation"></a><span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1947">Office.Licensing.FullValidation</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1947">Office.Licensing.FullValidation</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1948">To se prikupljaju u svakoj sesiji koja prijavljuje stanje licenciranja računala te prijavljuje pogreške koje se korisniku prikazuju i zbog kojih ne može koristiti aplikaciju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1948">This is collected on every session that reports the licensing state of the machine and reports the errors that the user is seeing due to which they are not able to use the application.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1949">Događaj označava je li korisnikovo računalo u dobrom stanju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1949">This event indicates if the user's machine is healthy or not.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1950">Za taj smo događaj postavili otkrivanje anomalija da bismo prepoznali uzrokuje li regresija ili mehanizam aktivacije negativno ponašanje korisnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1950">We have anomaly detection set up for this event to indicate if a regression or activation mechanism is causing bad user behavior.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1951">Ključno je i za dijagnosticiranje korisničkih problema te za praćenje stanja sustava.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1951">This is also critical when diagnosing user issues and for monitoring system health.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1952">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1952">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1953">**Acid** – GUID identifikator koji predstavlja proizvod sustava Office za koji korisnik ima licencu </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1953">**Acid** – A GUID identifier representing the Office product that the user is licensed for</span></span> 
  
  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1954">**Atributi Activationatribute**-vrsta mehanizma aktivacije koji korisnik upotrebljava.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1954">**ActivationAttributes** - Type of activation mechanism that the user is using.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1955">**IsSessionLicensing** – određuje je li trenutno pokrenut način rada za aktivaciju zajedničkog računala</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1955">**IsSessionLicensing** – Whether we are currently running under shared computer activation mode or not</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1956">**LicenseCategory** – kategorija licence za Office koju korisnik koristi </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1956">**LicenseCategory** – Category of the Office license that the user is using</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1957">**Licenses** – popis naziva svih licenci za Office koje postoje na računalu </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1957">**Licenses** – List of names of all the  Office licenses that are present on the machine</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1958">**LicenseStatuses** – status svih licenci za Office koje postoje na računalu </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1958">**LicenseStatuses** – Status of all the Office licenses present on the machine</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1963">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1963">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1964">**EntitlementCount** – Broj prava koja korisnik ima</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1964">**EntitlementCount** – Number of entitlements the user has</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1969">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1969">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensinginrfm"></a><span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1981">Office.Licensing.InRFM</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1981">Office.Licensing.InRFM</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensinginstallkey"></a><span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1990">Office.Licensing.InstallKey</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1990">Office.Licensing.InstallKey</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1998">U slučaju da uočimo probleme s tijekom rada aktivacije, pokrećemo čarobnjaka za licencu i šaljemo ovaj signal da ukazuje na isto.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1998">In case we see problems with the Activation workflow, we trigger a license wizard and send out this signal to indicate the same.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-1999">Ključno je radi otkrivanja je li korisnik u dobrom stanju te da mu ne nedostaje neka funkcija, koristi se u svrhe određivanja stanja sustava i za dijagnostiku ako korisnik prijavi problem s računalom</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-1999">It is critical in detecting if the user is in a good state and not missing functionality, used for system health and used for diagnostic purposes if a user reports an issue with their machine</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-2001">**Acid** – GUID identifikator koji predstavlja proizvod sustava Office za koji korisnik ima licencu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-2001">**Acid** - A GUID identifier representing the Office product that the user is licensed for</span></span>
