- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-2458">**AppInfo_Language** – Jezik pod kojim se aplikacija izvodi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-2458">**AppInfo_Language** - The language the application is running under</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-2459">**AppversionLong** – Verzija aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-2459">**AppVersionLong** - The application version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-2460">**Channel** – Preference za publiku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-2460">**Channel** - The preference for audience</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-2461">**Device_NetworkCountry** – Zemlja uređaja (na temelju IP adrese)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-2461">**Device_NetworkCountry** - The device country (based on IP address)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-2462">**DeviceID** – Identifikator uređaja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-2462">**DeviceID** - The device identifier</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-2463">**DeviceInfo_Model** – Hardverski model uređaja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-2463">**DeviceInfo_Model** - The hardware model of the device</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-2464">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** – Vrsta mreže (Wi-Fi, ožičena, nepoznata)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-2464">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** - The type of network (Wi-Fi, Wired, Unknown)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-2465">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** – Verzija operacijskog sustava</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-2465">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** - The version of the Operating System</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-2466">**Event_ReceivedTime** – Vrijeme primanja telemetrije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-2466">**Event_ReceivedTime** - The time at which telemetry was received</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-2467">**EventInfo_Name** – Naziv telemetrijskog događaja koji se zapisuje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-2467">**EventInfo_Name** - The name of the telemetry event being logged</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-2468">**EventInfo_Time** – Vrijeme odvijanja zapisanog događaja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-2468">**EventInfo_Time** - The time at which the logged event took place</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-2576">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** – Verzija operacijskog sustava</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-2576">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** - The version of the operating system</span></span>

### <a name="controller_alertmanager_tmpdiskfullretrycancel"></a><span data-ttu-id="72c2f-2648">controller_alertmanager_tmpdiskfullretrycancel</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-2648">controller_alertmanager_tmpdiskfullretrycancel</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-2651">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-2651">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-3589">**AppInfo_Language** – Jezik pod kojim se aplikacija izvodi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-3589">**AppInfo_Language** - The language the application is running under</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-3590">**AppVersionLong** – Verzija aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-3590">**AppVersionLong** - The application Version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-3596">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** – Verzija operacijskog sustava</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-3596">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** - The Version of the Operating System</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-3597">**Event_ReceivedTime** – Vrijeme primanja telemetrije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-3597">**Event_ReceivedTime** - The time at which telemetry was received</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-3598">**EventInfo_Name** – Naziv telemetrijskog događaja koji se zapisuje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-3598">**EventInfo_Name** - The name of the telemetry event being logged</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-3599">**EventInfo_Time** – Vrijeme odvijanja zapisanog događaja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-3599">**EventInfo_Time** - The time at which the logged event took place</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-3600">**HowTocheck** – Postavka za provjeru ažuriranja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-3600">**HowTocheck** - The preference for checking of updates</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-3601">**Payload** – Sadrži URL za preuzimanje te kôd pogreške u slučaju neuspjeha.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-3601">**Payload** - Contains download URL, and an error code in case of failure.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-3602">URL za preuzimanje je mjesto za preuzimanje Microsofta, osim ako je kanal postavljen na Prilagođeno.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-3602">Download URL is Microsoft download location except when the channel is set to Custom.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-3603">Za prilagođeni kanal ova je vrijednost postavljena na "Prilagođena lokacija".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-3603">For Custom channel, this value is set to "Custom Location".</span></span>

### <a name="downloadmanifest_configuration"></a><span data-ttu-id="72c2f-3607">downloadmanifest_configuration</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-3607">downloadmanifest_configuration</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-3613">**AppversionLong** – Verzija aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-3613">**AppVersionLong** - The application version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-3614">**Channel** – Preference za publiku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-3614">**Channel** - The preference for audience</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-3615">**Device_NetworkCountry** – Zemlja uređaja (na temelju IP adrese)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-3615">**Device_NetworkCountry** - The device country (based on IP address)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-3622">**EventInfo_Time** – Vrijeme odvijanja zapisanog događaja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-3622">**EventInfo_Time** - The time at which the logged event took place</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-3623">**Payload** – Označava je li pogreška povezana s postavljanjem prilagođenog poslužitelja ili instaliranim komponentama MAU-a</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-3623">**Payload** -Indicates whether error lies with custom server setup, or installed MAU components</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-3624">**PipelineInfo_ClientCountry** – Zemlja uređaja (na temelju IP adrese)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-3624">**PipelineInfo_ClientCountry** - The device country (based on IP address)</span></span>

### <a name="downloadtask_downloadfailure"></a><span data-ttu-id="72c2f-3969">downloadtask_downloadfailure</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-3969">downloadtask_downloadfailure</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-3970">Ovaj događaj evidentira da je došlo do pogreške prilikom preuzimanja datoteke paketa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-3970">This event logs that an error occurred downloading a package file.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-3971">Evidentiramo put ažuriranja te pogrešku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-3971">We log the update path and the error.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-3972">Ovaj događaj koristimo za osiguravanje da postupak ažuriranja funkcionira kako se očekuje i da pomogne u rješavanju pogrešaka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-3972">We use this event for ensuring the update process works as expected and to help troubleshoot errors.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-3976">**AppInfo_Language** – Jezik pod kojim se aplikacija izvodi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-3976">**AppInfo_Language** - The language the application is running under</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-3977">**AppVersionLong** – Verzija aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-3977">**AppVersionLong** - The application Version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-3978">**Channel** – Preference za publiku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-3978">**Channel** - The preference for audience</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-3979">**Device_NetworkCountry** – Zemlja uređaja (na temelju IP adrese)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-3979">**Device_NetworkCountry** - The device country (based on IP address)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-3980">**DeviceID** – Identifikator uređaja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-3980">**DeviceID** - The device identifier</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-3981">**DeviceInfo_Model** – Hardverski model uređaja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-3981">**DeviceInfo_Model** - The Hardware Model of the device</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-3982">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** – Vrsta mreže (Wi-Fi, ožičena, nepoznata)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-3982">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** - The type of network (Wi-Fi, Wired, Unknown)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-3983">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** – Verzija operacijskog sustava</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-3983">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** - The Version of the Operating System</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-3984">**Error** – Pogreška koja je uočena tijekom preuzimanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-3984">**Error** – The error observed during download.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-3985">**Event_ReceivedTime** – Vrijeme primanja telemetrije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-3985">**Event_ReceivedTime** - The time at which telemetry was received</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-3986">**EventInfo_Name** – Naziv telemetrijskog događaja koji se zapisuje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-3986">**EventInfo_Name** - The name of the telemetry event being logged</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-3987">**EventInfo_Time** – Vrijeme odvijanja zapisanog događaja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-3987">**EventInfo_Time** - The time at which the logged event took place</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-3988">**HowTocheck** – Postavka za provjeru ažuriranja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-3988">**HowTocheck** - The preference for checking of updates</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-3991">**PipelineInfo_ClientCountry** – Zemlja uređaja (na temelju IP adrese)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-3991">**PipelineInfo_ClientCountry** - The device country (based on IP address)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-3994">**UpdateID** – Identifikator ažuriranja koje se preuzima.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-3994">**UpdateID** – The identifier of the update being downloaded.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-4302">**DeviceID** – Identifikator uređaja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-4302">**DeviceID** - The device identifier</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-4303">**DeviceInfo_Model** – Hardverski model uređaja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-4303">**DeviceInfo_Model** - The Hardware Model of the device</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-4346">**AppversionLong** – Verzija aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-4346">**AppVersionLong** - The application version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-4350">**DeviceInfo_Model** – Hardverski model uređaja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-4350">**DeviceInfo_Model** - The hardware model of the device</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-4351">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** – Vrsta mreže (Wi-Fi, ožičena, nepoznata)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-4351">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** - The type of network (Wi-Fi, wired, unknown)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-4353">**Event_ReceivedTime** – Vrijeme primanja telemetrije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-4353">**Event_ReceivedTime** - The time at which telemetry was received</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-4354">**EventInfo_Name** – Naziv telemetrijskog događaja koji se zapisuje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-4354">**EventInfo_Name** - The name of the telemetry event being logged</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-4372">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** – Vrsta mreže (Wi-Fi, ožičena, nepoznata)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-4372">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** - The type of network (Wi-Fi, wired, unknown)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-4376">**EventInfo_Time** – Vrijeme odvijanja zapisanog događaja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-4376">**EventInfo_Time** -   The time at which the logged event took place</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-4390">**Channel** – Preference za publiku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-4390">**Channel** - The preference for audience</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-4394">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** – Vrsta mreže (Wi-Fi, ožičena, nepoznata)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-4394">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** - The type of network (Wi-Fi, wired, unknown)</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-4395">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** – Verzija operacijskog sustava</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-4395">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** - The version of the operating system</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-4397">**EventInfo_Name** – Naziv telemetrijskog događaja koji se zapisuje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-4397">**EventInfo_Name** - The name of the telemetry event being logged</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-4398">**EventInfo_Time** – Vrijeme odvijanja zapisanog događaja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-4398">**EventInfo_Time** -   The time at which the logged event took place</span></span> 
    
- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-4399">**HowToCheck** – Način provjere postavke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-4399">**HowToCheck** - How to check setting</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-4405">Ovaj događaj označava da Microsoftov pomoćnik za ažuriranja izdaje obavijest za ažuriranja na čekanju jer postoje otvorene registrirane aplikacije, a za instalaciju ažuriranja te će se aplikacije morati zatvoriti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-4405">This event indicates that the Microsoft Update Assistant is sending a notification for pending updates because there are registered applications open and updates will require the applications closed to proceed.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-4406">Ovim događajem utvrđujemo količinu ažuriranja za koje je potrebna radnja korisnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-4406">We use this event to determine volume of updates that require user intervention.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-4407">Ovim se događajem potiču poboljšanja korisničkog doživljaja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-4407">This event is used to help drive enhancement in user experience.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-4408">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-4408">The following fields are collected:</span></span>  

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-4409">**App** – Proces aplikacije za slanje događaja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-4409">**App** - The application process sending the event</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-4410">**AppInfo_Language** – Jezik pod kojim se aplikacija izvodi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-4410">**AppInfo_Language** - The language the application is running under</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-4695">**DeviceID** – Identifikator uređaja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-4695">**DeviceID** – The device identifier</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-4700">**EventInfo_Name** – Naziv telemetrijskog događaja koji se zapisuje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-4700">**EventInfo_Name** – The name of the telemetry event being logged</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-4702">**HowTocheck** – Postavka za provjeru ažuriranja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-4702">**HowTocheck** – The preference for checking of updates</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-5049">**Device_NetworkCountry** – Zemlja uređaja (na temelju IP adrese)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-5049">**Device_NetworkCountry** – The device country (based on IP address)</span></span>

### <a name="gui_updatemanager_applaunchduringupdate"></a><span data-ttu-id="72c2f-5322">gui_updatemanager_applaunchduringupdate</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-5322">gui_updatemanager_applaunchduringupdate</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-5323">Ovaj događaj izvješćuje da je aplikacija pokrenuta dok se ažurirala, a značajka Microsoftovo automatsko ažuriranje prekida pokrenutu aplikaciju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-5323">This event reports that an application was launched while it was being updated, and Microsoft AutoUpdate is terminating the launched application.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-5324">Napominjemo da pokretanje aplikacije dok se ona ažurira može dovesti do oštećenja aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-5324">Note that launching an application while being updated may result in application corruption.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-5325">Ovim događajem osiguravamo da pokretanje aplikacije ne utječe na proces ažuriranja prije no što ona ude spremna za upotrebu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-5325">We use this event to ensure update process is not impacted by launched application before it is ready to be used.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-5637">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-5637">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-5639">**App** – Proces aplikacije za slanje događaja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-5639">**App** - The application process sending the event</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-5640">**AppID** – Identifikator za aplikaciju koja se ažurira</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-5640">**AppID** - Identifier for the application being updated</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-5641">**AppInfo_Language** – Jezik pod kojim se aplikacija izvodi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-5641">**AppInfo_Language** - The language the application is running under</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-5642">**AppleEventClass** – Označava vrstu događaja koji se šalje/priznaje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-5642">**AppleEventClass** - Indicates type of event being sent/acknowledged</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-5643">**AppleEventID** – Jedinstveni identifikator događaja koji se šalje/priznaje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-5643">**AppleEventID** - Unique identifier for the event being sent/acknowledged</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-5645">**Channel** – Preference za publiku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-5645">**Channel** - The preference for audience</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-5646">**Device_NetworkCountry** – Zemlja uređaja (na temelju IP adrese)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-5646">**Device_NetworkCountry** - The device country (based on IP address)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-5647">**DeviceID** – Identifikator uređaja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-5647">**DeviceID** - The device identifier</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-5649">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** – Vrsta mreže (Wi-Fi, ožičena, nepoznata)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-5649">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** - The type of network (Wi-Fi, wired, unknown)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-5650">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** – Verzija operacijskog sustava</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-5650">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** - The version of the operating system</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-5651">**Event_ReceivedTime** – Vrijeme primanja telemetrije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-5651">**Event_ReceivedTime** - The time at which telemetry was received</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-5659">**Success** – Označava je li dotična aplikacija prijavila uspjeh operacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-5659">**Success** - Indicates whether the subject application has reported success of operation</span></span>

### <a name="updatestatus_codesign"></a><span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7713">UpdateStatus_Codesign</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7713">UpdateStatus_Codesign</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7714">Ovaj događaj izvješćuje o stanju potvrde suoblikovanja koje Microsoftov pomoćnik za ažuriranje pokreće nakon instalacije ažuriranja klijentskih aplikacija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7714">This event reports the status from codesign verification Microsoft Update Assistant runs after installing client application updates.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7715">Ovim događajem osiguravamo da pružamo pakete koji su valjani i nadogradit ćemo instaliranu aplikaciju na najnoviju verziju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7715">We use this event to ensure that we provide packages that are valid and will update the installed application to newest version.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7718">**AppID** – Identifikator za aplikaciju koja se ažurira</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7718">**AppID** - Identifier for the application being updated</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7719">**AppInfo_Language** – Jezik pod kojim se aplikacija izvodi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7719">**AppInfo_Language** - The language the application is running under</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7720">**AppversionLong** – Verzija aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7720">**AppVersionLong** - The application version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7721">**Channel** – Preference za publiku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7721">**Channel** - The preference for audience</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7750">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** – Vrsta mreže (Wi-Fi, ožičena, nepoznata)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7750">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** - The type of network (Wi-Fi, wired, unknown)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7908">Evidentiramo zahtjeve i odgovore primljene u web-servis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7908">We log requests and responses received into webservices.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7909">Ovaj događaj koristimo za osiguravanje da postupak ažuriranja funkcionira kako se očekuje i da pomogne u rješavanju pogrešaka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7909">We use this event for ensuring the update process works as expected and to help troubleshoot errors.</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7910">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7910">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7913">**AppVersionLong** – Verzija aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7913">**AppVersionLong** - The application Version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7914">**Channel** – Preference za publiku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7914">**Channel** - The preference for audience</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7915">**Device_NetworkCountry** – Zemlja uređaja (na temelju IP adrese)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7915">**Device_NetworkCountry** - The device country (based on IP address)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7916">**DeviceID** – Identifikator uređaja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7916">**DeviceID** - The device identifier</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7917">**DeviceInfo_Model** – Hardverski model uređaja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7917">**DeviceInfo_Model** - The Hardware Model of the device</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7918">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** – Vrsta mreže (Wi-Fi, ožičena, nepoznata)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7918">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** - The type of network (Wi-Fi, Wired, Unknown)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7919">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** – Verzija operacijskog sustava</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7919">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** - The Version of the Operating System</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7920">**Event_ReceivedTime** – Vrijeme primanja telemetrije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7920">**Event_ReceivedTime** - The time at which telemetry was received</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7921">**EventInfo_Name** – Naziv telemetrijskog događaja koji se zapisuje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7921">**EventInfo_Name** - The name of the telemetry event being logged</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7922">**EventInfo_Time** – Vrijeme odvijanja zapisanog događaja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7922">**EventInfo_Time** - The time at which the logged event took place</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7923">**HowTocheck** – Postavka za provjeru ažuriranja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7923">**HowTocheck** - The preference for checking of updates</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7924">**Payload** – Sadrži ID pozivatelja web-servisa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7924">**Payload** - Contains web-service caller ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7925">**PipelineInfo_ClientCountry** – Zemlja uređaja (na temelju IP adrese)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7925">**PipelineInfo_ClientCountry** - The device country (based on IP address)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7926">**PipelineInfo_ClientIp** – Prva 3 okteta IP adrese</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7926">**PipelineInfo_ClientIp** - The first 3 octets of the IP address</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7927">**SessionId** – Identifikator sesije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7927">**SessionId** - The identifier for the session</span></span>

### <a name="webservices_whatsnew"></a><span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7928">webservices_whatsnew</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7928">webservices_whatsnew</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7929">Ovaj se događaj aktivira kada Microsoftovo automatsko ažuriranje (MAU) provodi upit za web-usluge u značajci „Što je novo” za registrirane aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7929">This event is triggered when Microsoft Auto Update (MAU) queries web-services on the “what’s new” feature for registered applications.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7930">Ovim se događajem utvrđuje stanje značajke „Što je novo”.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7930">This event is used to determine health of the “what’s new” feature.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7932">**App** – Proces aplikacije koji šalje događaj</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7932">**App** -The application process sending the event</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7933">**AppInfo_Language** – Jezik pod kojim se aplikacija izvodi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7933">**AppInfo_Language** -The language the application is running under</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7934">**AppVersionLong** – Verzija aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7934">**AppVersionLong** -The application version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7935">**Channel** – Preference za publiku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7935">**Channel** -The preference for audience</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7936">**Device_NetworkCountry** – Zemlja uređaja (na temelju IP adrese)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7936">**Device_NetworkCountry** -The device country (based on IP address)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7937">**DeviceID** – Identifikator uređaja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7937">**DeviceID** -The device identifier</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7938">**DeviceInfo_Model** – Hardverski model uređaja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7938">**DeviceInfo_Model** -The hardware model of the device</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7939">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** – Vrsta mreže (Wi-Fi, ožičena, nepoznata)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7939">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** -The type of network (Wi-Fi, wired, unknown)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7940">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** – Verzija operacijskog sustava</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7940">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** -The version of the operating system</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7941">**Event_ReceivedTime** – Vrijeme primanja telemetrije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7941">**Event_ReceivedTime** -The time at which telemetry was received</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7942">**EventInfo_Name** – Naziv telemetrijskog događaja koji se zapisuje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7942">**EventInfo_Name** -The name of the telemetry event being logged</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7943">**EventInfo_Time** – Vrijeme odvijanja zapisanog događaja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7943">**EventInfo_Time** -The time at which the logged event took place</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7944">**HowToCheck** – Način provjere postavke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7944">**HowToCheck** -How to check setting</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7945">**Payload** – Sadrži informacije o broju aplikacija s informacijama o tome što je novo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7945">**Payload** -Contains information on number of applications with what’s new information</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7946">**PipelineInfo_ClientCountry** – Zemlja uređaja (na temelju IP adrese)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7946">**PipelineInfo_ClientCountry** -The device country (based on IP address)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7947">**PipelineInfo_ClientIp** – Prva tri okteta IP adrese</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7947">**PipelineInfo_ClientIp** -The first three octets of the IP address</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7948">**SessionId** – Identifikator sesije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7948">**SessionId** -The identifier for the session</span></span>

## <a name="onenote-sync-events"></a><span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7949">Sinkronizacija događaja u programu OneNote</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7949">OneNote sync events</span></span>

### <a name="officeonenotestoragenotebooksyncresult"></a><span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7950">Office.OneNote.Storage.NotebookSyncResult</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7950">Office.OneNote.Storage.NotebookSyncResult</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7951">Ovaj događaj zapisuje rezultat sinkronizacije bilježnice.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7951">This event logs notebook sync result.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7952">Koristi se za otkrivanje broja jedinstvenih ciljeva sinkronizacije tijekom izračuna rezultata sinkronizacije aplikacije OneNote.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7952">It is used for figuring out how many unique sync targets when calculating OneNote sync score.</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7953">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7953">The following fields are collected</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7954">**CachedError_Code** – numerirani ili alfanumerički kod koji se koristi za određivanje prirode predmemorirane pogreške i/ili razloga pojave</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7954">**CachedError_Code** - a numbered or alphanumeric code used to determine the nature of the cached error, and/or why it occurred</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7955">**CachedError_Description** – opis predmemorirane pogreške</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7955">**CachedError_Description** – a description of the cached error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7956">**CachedError_Tag** – označava mjesto na kojem se predmemorirana pogreška prikazuje u kodu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7956">**CachedError_Tag** – indicate where in the code throws the cached error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7957">**CachedError_Type** – vrsta predmemorirane pogreške, npr. Win32Error itd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7957">**CachedError_Type** – the type of the cached error, e.g. Win32Error, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7958">**ExecutionTime** – vrijeme u milisekundama potrebno za repliciranje bilježnice</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7958">**ExecutionTime** – time in milliseconds taken to replicate the notebook</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7959">**Gosid** – globalni ID prostora objekta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7959">**Gosid** – global object space ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7960">**IdentityType** – vrsta identiteta, npr. Windows Live, Org ID itd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7960">**IdentityType** – identity type, e.g. Windows Live, Org ID, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7961">**InitialReplicationInSession** – označava je li ova replikacija prva replikacija bilježnice nakon otvaranja ili nije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7961">**InitialReplicationInSession** – is this replication the first notebook replication after open or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7962">**IsBackgroundSync** – označava je li ovo sinkronizacija u pozadini ili nije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7962">**IsBackgroundSync** – is this a background sync or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7963">**IsCachedErrorSuppressed** – označava je li predmemorirana pogreška potisnuta ili nije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7963">**IsCachedErrorSuppressed** – is the cached error suppressed or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7964">**IsCachedErrorUnexpected** – označava je li predmemorirana pogreška neočekivana ili nije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7964">**IsCachedErrorUnexpected** – is the cached error unexpected or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7965">**IsNotebookErrorSuppressed** – označava je li pogreška sinkronizacije na razini bilježnice potisnuta ili nije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7965">**IsNotebookErrorSuppressed** – is the notebook level sync error suppressed or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7966">**IsNotebookErrorUnexpected** – označava je li pogreška sinkronizacije na razini bilježnice neočekivana ili nije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7966">**IsNotebookErrorUnexpected** – is the notebook level sync error unexpected or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7967">**IsSectionErrorSuppressed** – označava je li pogreška sinkronizacije odjeljka potisnuta ili nije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7967">**IsSectionErrorSuppressed** – is the section sync error suppressed or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7968">**IsSectionErrorUnexpected** – označava je li pogreška sinkronizacije odjeljka neočekivana ili nije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7968">**IsSectionErrorUnexpected** – is the section sync error unexpected or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7969">**IsUsingRealtimeSync** – označava koristi li sinkronizacija bilježnice suvremenu sinkronizaciju sadržaja stranice ili ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7969">**IsUsingRealtimeSync** – is the notebook sync using modern page content sync or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7970">**LastAttemptedSync** – vremenska oznaka za trenutak kada se proveo posljednji pokušaj sinkronizacije bilježnice</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7970">**LastAttemptedSync** – timestamp when the notebook was attempted to be synced last time</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7971">**LastBackgroundSync** – vremenska oznaka za trenutak kada se proveo posljednji pokušaj sinkronizacije u pozadini</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7971">**LastBackgroundSync** – timestamp when the latest background sync was attempted</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7972">**LastNotebookViewedDate** – datum kada je bilježnica posljednji put prikazana</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7972">**LastNotebookViewedDate** – the date when the notebook was last viewed</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7973">**LastSuccessfulSync** – vremenska oznaka za trenutak kada se bilježnica uspješno prethodno sinkronizirala</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7973">**LastSuccessfulSync** – timestamp when the notebook successfully synced before</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7974">**NeedToRestartBecauseOfInconsistencies** – treba li se sinkronizacija ponovno pokrenuti zbog nedosljednosti ili ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7974">**NeedToRestartBecauseOfInconsistencies** – does the sync need to restart because of inconsistencies or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7975">**NotebookErrorCode** – kod pogreške sinkronizacije na razini bilježnice spremljen je na prostoru grafikona bilježnice</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7975">**NotebookErrorCode** – notebook level sync error code saved on notebook graph space</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7976">**NotebookId** – ID bilježnice</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7976">**NotebookId** – notebook ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7977">**NotebookType** – vrsta bilježnice</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7977">**NotebookType** – notebook type</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7978">**ReplicatingAgainBecauseOfInconsistencies** – pokreće li se sinkronizacija ponovno zbog nedosljednosti ili ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7978">**ReplicatingAgainBecauseOfInconsistencies** – does the sync restart because of inconsistencies or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7979">**SectionError_Code** – numerirani ili alfanumerički kod koji se koristi za određivanje prirode pogreške sinkronizacije odjeljka i/ili razloga pojave</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7979">**SectionError_Code** – a numbered or alphanumeric code used to determine the nature of the section sync error, and/or why it occurred</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7980">**SectionError_Description** – opis pogreške sinkronizacije odjeljka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7980">**SectionError_Description** – a description of the section sync error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7981">**SectionError_Tag** – označava mjesto na kojem se pogreška sinkronizacije odjeljka prikazuje u kodu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7981">**SectionError_Tag** – indicate where in the code throws the section sync error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7982">**SectionError_Type** – vrsta pogreške sinkronizacije odjeljka, npr. Win32Error itd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7982">**SectionError_Type** – the type of the section sync error, e.g. Win32Error, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7983">**Success** – je li bilježnica uspješno sinkronizirana ili nije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7983">**Success** – is the notebook sync successful or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7984">**SyncDestinationType** – vrsta odredišta sinkronizacije, npr. OneDrive ili SharePoint Online</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7984">**SyncDestinationType** – sync destination type, i.e. OneDrive or SharePoint Online</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7985">**SyncId** – broj jedinstven svakoj sinkronizaciji bilježnice</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7985">**SyncId** – a number unique to each notebook sync</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7986">**SyncWasFirstInSession** – označava je li ova sinkronizacija prva sinkronizacija u trenutnoj sesiji</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7986">**SyncWasFirstInSession** – is this sync the first sync in current session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7987">**SyncWasUserInitiated** – označava je li korisnik sinkronizacije pokrenut ili nije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7987">**SyncWasUserInitiated** – is this sync user initiated or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7988">**TenantId** – ID klijenta sustava SharePoint</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7988">**TenantId** – SharePoint tenant ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7989">**TimeSinceLastAttemptedSync** – vrijeme proteklo od posljednjeg pokušaja sinkronizacije bilježnice</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7989">**TimeSinceLastAttemptedSync** – time since last notebook sync attempt</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7990">**TimeSinceLastSuccessfulSync** – vrijeme proteklo od posljednje uspješne sinkronizacije bilježnice</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7990">**TimeSinceLastSuccessfulSync** – time since last successful notebook sync</span></span>

### <a name="officeonenotestoragerealtimewebsocketsessioninfo"></a><span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7991">Office.OneNote.Storage.RealTime.WebSocketSessionInfo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7991">Office.OneNote.Storage.RealTime.WebSocketSessionInfo</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-7992">Ovaj događaj evidentira rezultat sinkronizacije web-utičnice za obje sinkronizacije aplikacije OneNote: suvremenu sinkronizaciju sadržaja stranice i suvremenu sinkronizaciju hijerarhije. Koristi se za otkrivanje broja jedinstvenih ciljeva sinkronizacije tijekom izračuna rezultata sinkronizacije aplikacije OneNote.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-7992">This event logs WebSocket sync result for both OneNote modern page content sync modern hierarchy sync. ### <a name="onenotestorageconnectivitychanged"></a><span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8077">OneNote.Storage.ConnectivityChanged</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8077">OneNote.Storage.ConnectivityChanged</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8078">Događaj se evidentira bez obzira da li korisnik ima vezu sa internetom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8078">The event logs if a user has internet connectivity or not.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8079">Ta se funkcija koristi za povezivanje ostalih metrika performansi sinkronizacije i omogućuje nam ignoriranje događaja koji se javljaju dok korisnik ne koristi internetsku vezu jer ne očekujemo da će naše kašnjenje usluge biti prihvatljivo bez povezivanja s internetom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8079">This is used to correlate the other sync health performance metrics by allowing us to ignore events that occur while a user does not have internet connectivity as we do not expect our service latency to be acceptable without internet connectivity.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8080">To nam omogućuje izračun točnog broja sesija za naš metrički broj na kriške korisnika (po-klijentu, po-sektorima).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8080">This allows us to calculate an accurate session count for our metrics across slices of customers (per-tenant, per-sector).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8081">Pomoću nje možemo filtrirati i izvješća o pogreškama jer postoje brojne pogreške pri sinkronizaciji za koje očekujemo da će se pojavljivati bez mrežnog povezivanja, ali ta istraga ne jamči ništa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8081">We also use it to filter error reports as there are numerous sync errors that we expect to occur without network connectivity but that warrant investigation otherwise.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8082">Ako ne primimo te podatke ne možemo točno nadgledati performanse proizvoda ili odrediti hoće li se očekivati pogreške koje je iskusio korisnik ili zahtijevati daljnju istragu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8082">If we do not receive this data, we will not be able to accurately monitor our products performance or determine if errors experienced by a user are expected or require further investigation.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8083">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8083">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8084">**InternetConnectivityNowAvailable** – ako je stanje povezivanja izmijenjeno, pa je sada Internet</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8084">**InternetConnectivityNowAvailable** -  If the connectivity state has been changed so it is now Internet</span></span>

### <a name="onenotestoragelegacyinboundlatency"></a><span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8085">OneNote.Storage.LegacyInboundLatency</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8085">OneNote.Storage.LegacyInboundLatency</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8086">Kritični znak koji se koristi za praćenje operacija ulaznog sinkroniziranja koje komuniciraju izravno sa SharePoint sustavom, uključujući povezane informacije koje omogućuju praćenje i istraživanje performansi prijenosa podataka iz naše usluge.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8086">The critical signal used to track the performance of inbound sync operations that communicate directly with SharePoint including correlating information allowing us to monitor and investigate the performance of uploading data to our service.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8087">Ovaj se signal prikuplja samo za najgoru izvedbu u posljednjih 300 sekundi (broj sekundi može biti konfiguriran od strane Microsoft Corporation, ovisno o performansama i uvjetu usluge).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8087">This signal is only collected for the worst performing download in the last 300 seconds (the number of seconds is configurable by Microsoft depending on service performance and condition).</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8088">To se koristi da bi se osiguralo stanje usluge omogućujući nam da vidimo koji klijenti proživljavaju neprihvatljivo spore ulazne podatke za našu uslugu, informacije o podacima koje šalju kada su doživjeli spor ulaz i koliko je rasprostranjen problem s kašnjenjem unutar klijenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8088">This is used to ensure service health by allowing us to see which tenants are experiencing an unacceptably slow inbound of data to our service, information about the data they are uploading when they experienced the slow inbound and how widespread within a tenant that latency issue is.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8089">Također se koristi za izvješćivanje o stanju i performansama servisa u svim našim korisnicima radi mjerenja trendova tijekom vremena i automatskog uzbunjivanja pitanja za inženjersko ublažavanje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8089">It is also used to report service health and performance across our customers to measure trends over time and alert on issues automatically for engineering mitigation.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8090">Ako nemamo te podatke, to će nas spriječiti da osiguravamo odgovarajuće performanse kada se sinkronizacije korisnika promijene iz sustavu SharePoint na njihovo računalo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8090">If we do not have this data it will prevent us from ensuring adequate download performance when a user syncs changes from SharePoint to their computer.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8091">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8091">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8092">**IsEducationNotebook** – Booleova vrijednost koja ukazuje je li bilježnica za obrazovanje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8092">**IsEducationNotebook** - A bool indicating if the notebook is an education notebook</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8093">**SectionId** – ID bilježnice čiji je dio ovaj prijenos</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8093">**NotebookId** - The ID of the notebook that this upload is part of</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8094">**TimeToConfirmSyncedWithServerInMs** – vrijeme u milisekundama koje je potrebno za obavljanje prijenosa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8094">**TimeToConfirmSyncedWithServerInMs** - The time in milliseconds it took to perform the upload</span></span>

### <a name="onenotestoragelegacyoutboundlatency"></a><span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8095">OneNote.Storage.LegacyOutboundLatency</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8095">OneNote.Storage.LegacyOutboundLatency</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8096">Kritični znak koji se koristi za praćenje performansi operacija odlaznog sinkroniziranja koje komuniciraju izravno sa SharePoint sustavom, uključujući povezane informacije koje omogućuju praćenje i istraživanje performansi prijenosa podataka iz naše usluge.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8096">The critical signal used to track the performance of outbound sync operations that communicate directly with SharePoint including correlating information allowing us to monitor and investigate the performance of uploading data to our service.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8097">Ovaj se signal prikuplja samo za najgoru izvedbu u posljednjih 300 sekundi (broj sekundi može biti konfiguriran od strane Microsoft Corporation, ovisno o performansama i uvjetu usluge).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8097">This signal is only collected for the worst performing download in the last 300 seconds (the number of seconds is configurable by Microsoft depending on service performance and condition).</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8098">To se koristi da bi se osiguralo stanje usluge omogućujući nam da vidimo koji klijenti proživljavaju neprihvatljivo spore izlazne podatke ka našoj usluzi, informacije o podacima koje su slali kada su doživjeli spor izlaz i koliko je rasprostranjen problem s kašnjenjem unutar klijenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8098">This is used to ensure service health by allowing us to see which tenants are experiencing an unacceptably slow outbound of data to our service, information about the data they were uploading when they experienced the slow outbound and how widespread within a tenant that latency issue is.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8099">Također se koristi za izvješćivanje o stanju i performansama servisa u svim našim korisnicima radi mjerenja trendova tijekom vremena i automatskog uzbunjivanja pitanja za inženjersko ublažavanje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8099">It is also used to report service health and performance across our customers to measure trends over time and alert on issues automatically for engineering mitigation.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8100">Ako nemamo te podatke, to će nas spriječiti da osiguravamo odgovarajuće performanse kada se sinkronizirajući korisnici promijene u sustavu SharePoint.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8100">If we do not have this data, it will prevent us from ensuring adequate performance when syncing users changes up to SharePoint.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8101">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8101">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8102">**IsEducationNotebook** – Booleova vrijednost koja ukazuje je li bilježnica za obrazovanje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8102">**IsEducationNotebook** - A bool indicating if the notebook is an education notebook</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8103">**SectionId** – ID bilježnice čiji je dio ovaj prijenos</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8103">**NotebookId** - The ID of the notebook that this upload is part of</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8104">**TimeToConfirmSyncedWithServerInMs** – vrijeme u milisekundama koje je potrebno za obavljanje prijenosa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8104">**TimeToConfirmSyncedWithServerInMs** - The time in milliseconds it took to perform the upload</span></span>

### <a name="onenotestoragerealtimefiledataobjectdownload"></a><span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8105">OneNote.Storage.RealTime.FileDataObjectDownload</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8105">OneNote.Storage.RealTime.FileDataObjectDownload</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8106">Kritični signal koji se koristi za praćenje performansi kada korisnik upisuje objekt podataka datoteke (npr. umetnuta datoteka ili slika) koja se preuzima izravno iz našeg servisa, a ne u sklopu postupka sinkronizacije na stranici, u odjeljku ili u bilježnici.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8106">The critical signal used to track performance when a user inbounds a file data object (i.e. an embedded file or image) which is downloaded directly from our service and not as part of a sync operation on a page, section or notebook.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8107">Ovaj se signal prikuplja samo za najgoru izvedbu u posljednjih 300 sekundi (broj sekundi može biti konfiguriran od strane Microsoft Corporation, ovisno o performansama i uvjetu usluge).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8107">This signal is only collected for the worst performing download in the last 300 seconds (the number of seconds is configurable by Microsoft depending on service performance and condition).</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8108">To se koristi da bi se osiguralo stanje usluge i performanse omogućujući nam da vidimo koji klijenti proživljavaju neprihvatljivo sporo preuzimanje podataka iz naše usluge, i koliko je rasprostranjen problem s kašnjenjem unutar klijenta, te izvještava o našem ponašanju tijekom vremena i omogućuje nam da mjerimo trendove performansi usluge.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8108">This is used to ensure service health and performance by allowing us to see which tenants are experiencing an unacceptably slow download of data from our service, and how widespread within a tenant that latency issue is, and report our behavior over time allowing us to measure service performance trends.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8109">Ako vam se prikaže neprihvatljivo kašnjenje za objekt datoteke, te ćemo podatke koristiti i za povezivanje s drugim signalima klijenta i servisa koji se tiču objekta radi poboljšanja našeg procesa preuzimanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8109">If we see an unacceptable latency for a file object, we will also use this data to correlate that with other signals from the client and service regarding the object to make improvements to our download process.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8110">Podijelili smo i podatke na temelju proširenja preuzetog objekta datoteke kao što imamo različita očekivanja koja se temelje na tome je li datoteka prikazana u okviru našeg platna (npr. slika) ili je datoteka koja se ne umetne u obliku te podatke, onemogućit će nam praćenje performansi tih preuzimanja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8111">If we do not receive this data, it will prevent us from monitoring the performance of these downloads</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8112">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8112">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8113">**Datoteka** – veličina datoteke preuzete u bajtovima</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8113">**FileSizeInBytes** - The size of the file being downloaded in bytes</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8114">**IsImage** – A Booleova vrijednost koja određuje je li preuzeta datoteka ima proširenje koje se podudara s unaprijed definiranim popisom uobičajenih formata slika (.bmp, .emf, .gif, .jpe, .jpeg, .jpg, .png) koje smo prikazali u sklopu platna</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8114">**IsImage** - A bool determining if the file being downloaded has an extension that matches a pre-determined list of common image formats (.bmp, .emf, .gif, .jpe, .jpeg, .jpg, .png) that we display inline in the canvas</span></span>

### <a name="onenotestoragerealtimewebsocketdownload"></a><span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8116">OneNote.Storage.RealTime.WebSocketDownload</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8116">OneNote.Storage.RealTime.WebSocketDownload</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8117">Ključni znak koji se koristi za praćenje performansi ulaznog sinkroniziranja sustava, uključujući povezane podatke koji omogućuju praćenje i proučavanje performansi preuzimanja podataka iz našeg servisa (onenote.com).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8117">The critical signal used to track performance of inbound sync operations including correlating information allowing us to monitor and investigate the performance of downloading data from our service (onenote.com).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8118">Ovaj se signal prikuplja samo za najgoru izvedbu u posljednjih 300 sekundi (broj sekundi može biti konfiguriran od strane Microsoft Corporation, ovisno o performansama i uvjetu usluge).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8118">This signal is only collected for the worst performing download in the last 300 seconds (the number of seconds is configurable by Microsoft depending on service performance and condition).</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8119">To se koristi da bi se osiguralo stanje usluge omogućujući nam da vidimo koji klijenti proživljavaju neprihvatljivo spore ulazne podatke iz naše usluge, informacije o podacima koje su preuzimali kada su doživjeli spor ulaz i koliko je rasprostranjen problem s kašnjenjem unutar klijenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8119">This is used to ensure service health by allowing us to see which tenants are experiencing an unacceptably slow inbound of data from our service, information about the data they were downloading when they experienced the slow inbound and how widespread within a tenant that latency issue is.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8120">Također se koristi za izvješćivanje o stanju i performansama servisa u svim našim korisnicima radi mjerenja trendova tijekom vremena i automatskog uzbunjivanja pitanja za inženjersko ublažavanje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8120">It is also used to report service health and performance across our customers to measure trends over time and alert on issues automatically for engineering mitigation.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8121">Ako vidimo neprihvatljivo kašnjenje za odjeljak ili bilježnicu, te ćemo podatke koristiti i za povezivanje s drugim signalima klijenta i usluge koji se odnose na isti dokument radi identificiranja regresija performansi na strani klijenta koja nam omogućuje da isporučimo uslugu s boljim performansama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8121">If we see an unacceptable latency for a section or notebook we will also use this data to correlate that with other signals from the client and service regarding the same document to identify client side performance regressions allowing us to deliver a more performant service.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8122">Ako ne primimo te podatke, nećemo moći pratiti performanse tog aspekta naše usluge ni učinak promjena na strani poslužitelja koje možda smatramo potrebnim zbog korištenja ili drugih faktora.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8122">If we do not receive this data, we will be unable to monitor the performance of this aspect of our service, or the impact of server side changes we may find necessary due to usage or other factors.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8123">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8123">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8124">**DeviceSessionId**  – ID sesije uređaja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8124">**DeviceSessionId** -  The ID of the device session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8125">**IsEducationNotebook** – Booleova vrijednost koja ukazuje je li bilježnica za obrazovanje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8125">**IsEducationNotebook** - A bool indicating if the notebook is an education notebook</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8126">**IsHierarchyResource** – Booleova vrijednost koja ukazuje da li je resurs hijerarhijski</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8126">**IsHierarchyResource** - A bool indicating if the resource is a hierarchy resource</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8127">**SectionId** – ID bilježnice čiji je dio ovaj prijenos</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8127">**NotebookId** - The ID of the notebook that this upload is part of</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8128">**ResourceId** – ID resursa koji prenosimo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8128">**ResourceId** - The ID of the resource that we are uploading</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8129">**SectionId** – ID odjeljka čiji je dio ovaj prijenos</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8129">**SectionId** - The ID of the section that this upload is part of</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8130">**ServerSessionId** – ID sesije poslužitelja čiji je dio ovaj prijenos</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8130">**ServerSessionId** - The ID of the server session that this upload is part of</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8131">**TimeToConfirmSyncedWithServerInMs** – vrijeme u milisekundama između korisnika koji se nalazi na stranici i stoga replikacije koji potvrduje da se stranica sinkronizira s poslužiteljem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8131">**TimeToConfirmSyncedWithServerInMs** - The time in milliseconds between a user navigating to a page and the replication stack confirming that page is in sync with the server.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8132">**TimeToFirstUpdateInMs** – vrijeme u milisekundama između sustava za sinkronizaciju koji počinje ulaznu replikaciju stranice te funkcije replikacije pri sinkronizaciji s stanjem poslužitelja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8132">**TimeToFirstUpdateInMs** - The time in milliseconds between the sync engine beginning inbound replication of a page and that replication operation reaching the in sync with the server state.</span></span>

### <a name="onenotestoragerealtimewebsocketupload"></a><span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8133">OneNote.Storage.RealTime.WebSocketUpload</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8133">OneNote.Storage.RealTime.WebSocketUpload</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8134">Ključni znak koji se koristi za praćenje performansi ulaznog sinkroniziranja sustava, uključujući povezane informacije koje omogućuju praćenje i proučavanje performansi preuzimanja podataka iz našeg servisa (onenote.com).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8134">The critical signal used to track the performance of outbound sync operations including correlating information allowing us to monitor and investigate the performance of uploading data to our service (onenote.com)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8135">To se koristi da bi se osiguralo stanje usluge omogućujući nam da vidimo koji klijenti proživljavaju neprihvatljivo spore izlazne podatke ka našoj usluzi, informacije o podacima koje su slali kada su doživjeli spor izlaz i koliko je rasprostranjen problem s kašnjenjem unutar klijenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8135">This is used to ensure service health by allowing us to see which tenants are experiencing an unacceptably slow outbound of data to our service, information about the data they were uploading when they experienced the slow outbound and how widespread within a tenant that latency issue is.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8136">Također se koristi za izvješćivanje o stanju i performansama servisa u svim našim korisnicima radi mjerenja trendova tijekom vremena i automatskog uzbunjivanja pitanja za inženjersko ublažavanje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8136">It is also used to report service health and performance across our customers to measure trends over time and alert on issues automatically for engineering mitigation.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8137">Te ćemo podatke koristiti i za praćenje učinka i djelotvornosti poboljšanja koja smo napravili klijentima i uslugama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8137">We will also use this data to track the impact and effectiveness of improvements we make to our clients and services.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8138">Ako vidimo neprihvatljivo kašnjenje za odjeljak ili bilježnicu, te ćemo podatke koristiti i za povezivanje s drugim signalima klijenta i usluge koji se odnose na isti dokument radi identificiranja regresija performansi koja nam omogućuje da isporučimo doživljaj s boljim performansama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8138">If we see an unacceptable latency for a section or notebook we will also use this data to correlate that with other signals from the client and service regarding the same document to identify performance regressions allowing us to deliver a more performant experience.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8139">Ako ne primimo te podatke, nećemo moći pratiti performanse tog aspekta naše usluge ni učinak promjena na strani poslužitelja koje možda smatramo potrebnim zbog korištenja ili drugih faktora.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8139">If we do not receive this data, we will be unable to monitor the performance of this aspect of our service, or the impact of server side changes we may find necessary due to usage or other factors.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8140">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8140">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8141">**DeviceSessionId** – ID sesije uređaja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8141">**DeviceSessionId** - The ID of the device session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8142">**IsEducationNotebook** – Booleova vrijednost koja ukazuje je li bilježnica za obrazovanje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8142">**IsEducationNotebook** - A bool indicating if the notebook is an education notebook</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8143">**IsHierarchyResource** – Booleova vrijednost koja ukazuje da li je resurs hijerarhijski</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8143">**IsHierarchyResource** - A bool indicating if the resource is a hierarchy resource</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8144">**IsWorstTime** – Booleova vrijednost koji upućuje na to da li je vrijeme redovnog prijenosa događaja obično ili najgore vrijeme koje smo vidjeli na tom klijentu u posljednjih 300 sekundi (broj sekundi može biti konfiguriran od strane Microsoft Corporation ovisno o performansama i uvjetu usluge).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8144">**IsWorstTime** - A bool indicating if the time is a regular upload event, or the worst time we saw on this client in the last 300 seconds (the number of seconds is configurable by Microsoft depending on service performance and condition).</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8145">**SectionId** – ID bilježnice čiji je dio ovaj prijenos</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8145">**NotebookId** - The ID of the notebook that this upload is part of</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8146">**RecommendedPutIntervalInMs** – vrijeme koje je servis prenio klijentu kao preporučeno vremensko razdoblje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8146">**RecommendedPutIntervalInMs** - The time the service has communicated to the client as its recommended put interval</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8147">**ResourceId** – ID resursa koji prenosimo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8147">**ResourceId** - The ID of the resource that we are uploading</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8148">**SectionId** – ID odjeljka čiji je dio ovaj prijenos</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8148">**SectionId** - The ID of the section that this upload is part of</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8149">**SenderRequestId** – ID pošiljaoca koji izvršava prijenos</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8149">**SenderRequestId** - The ID of the sender performing the upload</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8150">**ServerSessionId** – ID sesije poslužitelja čiji je dio ovaj prijenos</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8150">**ServerSessionId** - The ID of the server session that this upload is part of</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8151">**UploadNonSuspendedTimeInMs** – vrijeme u milisekundama koje je potrebno za izvršavanje prijenosa izuzevši vrijeme kada je aplikacija suspendirana</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8151">**UploadNonSuspendedTimeInMs** - The time in milliseconds it took to perform the upload excluding the time when the application was suspended</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8152">**UploadTimeInMs** – vrijeme u milisekundama koje je potrebno za obavljanje prijenosa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8152">**UploadTimeInMs** - The time in milliseconds it took to actually perform the upload</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8153">**WaitTimeInMs** – vrijeme u milisekundama između zatraženog prijenosa i pokretanja prijenosa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8153">**WaitTimeInMs** - The time in milliseconds between an upload being requested and an upload starting</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8154">**WebUrl** – Web URL prijenosa (prijavljeni kao PiiWz)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8154">**WebUrl** - The WebUrl of the upload (Logged as a PiiWz)</span></span>

### <a name="onenotestoragesynchealth"></a><span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8155">OneNote.Storage.SyncHealth</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8155">OneNote.Storage.SyncHealth</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8156">Ključni znak koji se koristi za praćenje pogrešaka i iznimki koje su se dogodile unutar stoga za sinkronizaciju u klijentu programa OneNote koji nam omogućuje praćenje i ublažavanje tih neočekivanih uvjeta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8156">The critical signal used to track errors and exceptions that have occurred inside the sync stack in the OneNote client allowing us to monitor and mitigate these unexpected conditions.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8157">To se koristi da bi se osiguralo stanje servisa omogućujući nam pregled izvješća o pogreškama od klijenta u bliskoj stvarnom vremenu, što nam omogućuje odgovaranje na probleme sa sinkronizacijom tijekom njihove pojave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8157">This is used to ensure service health by allowing us to see error reports from the clients in near real-time, which lets us respond to sync issues as they arise.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8158">Također se koristi da bi se utvrdilo koliko je rasprostranjen problem te koliko je ozbiljan, unakrsnim referenciranjem oznake pogreške s klijentskim kodom da bi se utvrdio izvor pogreške.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8158">It is also used to identify how widespread an issue is, and how severe by cross-referencing the error tag with the client code to identify the source of failure.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8159">Također smo skupili te podatke da bismo dobili informacije o našim performansama tijekom vremena i utjecaju i djelotvornosti poboljšanja koja dajemo klijentima i uslugama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8159">We also aggregate this data to get information on our performance over time and the impact and effectiveness of improvements we make to our clients and services.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8160">Ako nemamo te podatke, nećemo moći proaktivno reagirati na uvjete pogreške u našem servisu za sinkronizaciju bez porasta eskalacije korisnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8160">If we do not have this data, we won’t be able to proactively respond to error conditions in our sync service without customer escalation.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8161">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8161">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8162">**Service** – servis za sinkronizaciju koji je klijent koristio kada se dogodila pogreška (naslijeđena ili moderna sinkronizacija)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8162">**Service** - The sync service the client was using when the error occurred (Legacy or Modern Sync)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8163">**Tag** – Oznaka (identifikacijska vrijednost) koja predstavlja pogrešku na koju je klijent naišao tijekom postupka sinkronizacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8163">**Tag** - The tag (an identifying value) representing the error that the client encountered during the sync operation</span></span>

Wi-Fi, izvanmrežni rad, 3G</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8167">**NetworkConnection** - Logs the connection type that the device is currently on e.g. Wi-Fi, offline, 3G</span></span>

Wi-Fi, izvanmrežni rad, 3G</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8173">**NetworkConnection** - Logs the connection type that the device is currently on e.g. Wi-Fi, offline, 3G</span></span>

### <a name="officeandroiddocsuiviewspaywalloperationmetrics"></a><span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8178">Office.Android.DocsUI.Views.PaywallOperationMetrics</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8178">Office.Android.DocsUI.Views.PaywallOperationMetrics</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8179">Microsoft to koristi za dobivanje ispravnosti značajke, uspjeha ili stope pogrešaka za korisnike pri kupnjama, kako bi osigurao odgovarajuća ulaganja za poboljšanje korisničkog iskustva kupca na mobilnim platformama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8179">Microsoft uses this to get the health of the feature, success, or error rates for the user for purchases, to ensure appropriate investments to improve the customers’ purchase experience across mobile platforms.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8180">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8180">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

### <a name="office_firstrun_apple_telemetryoptin"></a><span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8184">Office_FirstRun_Apple_TelemetryOptIn</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8184">Office_FirstRun_Apple_TelemetryOptIn</span></span>
