<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8188">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8188">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8189">**Data_EventId** – Kôd koji pokazuje preferenciju prikupljanja podataka koju je odabrao korisnik.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8189">**Data_EventId** – A code indicating the diagnostic data collection preference selected by the user.</span></span>

### <a name="officeiospaywallprovisioningresponse"></a><span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8190">Office.iOS.Paywall.Provisioning.Response</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8190">Office.iOS.Paywall.Provisioning.Response</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8191">Telemetrija proizvoda koja se upotrebljava za usklađivanje podataka o transakcijama kupnje s Microsoftovim sustavom trgovine radi omogućivanja povezanih pogodnosti pretplate.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8191">Product telemetry used for reconciliation of purchase transaction information with the Microsoft commerce system to enable associated subscription benefits.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8192">Koristi se za olakšavanje evidentiranja transakcija i omogućavanja pretplate za buduću referencu i interno usklađivanje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8192">Used to facilitate the transaction logging and subscription provisioning for future reference and internal reconciliation.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8193">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8193">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8194">**entryPoint** – niz – gumb/tijek s kojeg je prikazan Paywall.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8194">**entryPoint** - String – The Button/Flow from which Paywall was displayed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8195">Kao što je "Premium Upgrade Button" ili „First run flow“</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8195">Like “Premium Upgrade Button” or “First Run Flow”.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8196">**failureReason** – niz – dodan samo kada je status "neuspjeh".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8196">**failureReason** - String – Only added when status is “failure”.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8197">Ukazuje na odgovor na pogrešku koji je dao RFS.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8197">Indicating the error response given by the RFS Provisioning response.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8198">**productId** – niz – ID proizvoda trgovine App Store za koji je izrađen zahtjev</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8198">**productId** - String – App Store ID of the product the request was made for</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8199">**stanje** – niz – uspjeh ili neuspjeh, što upućuje na to je li zahtjev uspio ili ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8199">**status** - String – Success or Failure, indicating if the request succeeded or failed</span></span>


### <a name="officeiospaywallstorekitresponse"></a><span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8200">Office.iOS.Paywall.StoreKit.Response</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8200">Office.iOS.Paywall.StoreKit.Response</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8201">Podaci se prikupljaju kao kritična inženjerska telemetrija za bilježenje rezultata pokušaja kupnje koji je korisnik pokrenuo ručno.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8201">The data is collected as critical engineering telemetry to log the result of purchase attempt triggered manually by user.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8202">Telemetrija proizvoda upotrebljava se za usklađivanje podataka o transakcijama kupnje s Microsoftovim sustavom trgovine radi omogućivanja povezanih pogodnosti pretplate.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8202">The product telemetry is used for reconciliation of purchase transaction information with the Microsoft commerce system to enable associated subscription benefits.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8203">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8203">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8204">**entryPoint** – niz – gumb/tijek s kojeg je prikazan Paywall.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8204">**entryPoint** - String – The Button/Flow from which Paywall was displayed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8205">Kao što je "Premium Upgrade Button" ili „First run flow“</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8205">Like “Premium Upgrade Button” or “First Run Flow”.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8206">**failureReason** – niz – dodan samo kada je status "neuspjeh".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8206">**failureReason** - String – Only added when status is “failure”.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8207">Ukazuje na odgovor na pogrešku koji je dala trgovina App-store.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8207">Indicating the error response given by the App-store response</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8208">**productId** – niz – samo za „MakePurchase“, „PendingPurchase”, ID proizvoda trgovine app-store za koji je zahtjev stvoren.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8208">**productId** - String – Only for “MakePurchase”, “PendingPurchase”, the app-store ID of the product for which the request was made.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8209">**productsCount** -Int – samo za "ProductsFetch", broj proizvoda koje trgovina vraća.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8209">**productsCount** - Int – Only for “ProductsFetch”, the number of products returned by Store.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8210">**requestType** – niz – vrsta zahtjeva za Storekit.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8210">**requestType** - String – Type of StoreKit request.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8211">Kao što je "ProductsFetch", "Pendingpurchase"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8211">Like “ProductsFetch”, “PendingPurchase”</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8212">**status** – niz – uspjeh ili neuspjeh, što upućuje na uspjeh ili neuspjeh zahtjeva</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8212">**status** - String – Success or Failure, indicating success or failure of the request</span></span>


### <a name="officesystemgracefulexitgracefulappexitdesktop"></a><span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8213">Office.System.GracefulExit.GracefulAppExitDesktop</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8213">Office.System.GracefulExit.GracefulAppExitDesktop</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8214">Događaj je aktiviralo skladno ukidanje aplikacije za klijentske aplikacije sustava Office, kao što su, no ne ograničavajući se na Word, Excel, PowerPoint i Outlook.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8214">The event is triggered by a graceful application termination for Office client applications such as, but not limited to, Word, Excel, PowerPoint, and Outlook.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8215">Parametre skladnog zatvaranja upotrebljavamo za mjerenje stanja proizvoda klijenata sustava Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8215">We use Graceful Exit to measure the health of Office client products.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8216">To je zamišljeno da bude signal ključan za poslovanje koji inženjeri sustava Office koriste za postizanje stabilnosti proizvoda.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8216">It is intended to be a business-critical signal used by Office engineers to infer product stability.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8217">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8217">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8218">**AppBuild** – identifikator međuverzije zahvaćenog procesa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8218">**AppBuild** - Build version identifier for the affected process.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8219">**AppMajor** – identifikator glavne verzije zahvaćenog procesa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8219">**AppMajor** - Major version identifier for the affected process.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8220">**AppMinor** – identifikator sporedne verzije zahvaćenog procesa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8220">**AppMinor** - Minor version identifier for the affected process.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8221">**AppRevision** – identifikator međuverzije zahvaćenog procesa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8221">**AppRevision** - Build version identifier for the affected process.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8222">**Boot Completed** – dovršio je postupak pokretanja sustava Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8222">**BootCompleted** – Did Office process complete boot.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8223">**DetectionTime** – vrijeme otkrivanja neočekivanog zatvaranja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8223">**DetectionTime** - The time when the unexpected exit was detected.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8224">**EcsETag** – identifikator eksperimenta za postupak.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8224">**EcsETag** - An experiment identifier for the process.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8225">**HasEdit** – uređivanje dokumenta koje se pojavljuje tijekom postupka sustava Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8225">**HasEdit** – Was document editing occurring during the Office process.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8226">**HasOpen** – dokument je bio otvoren tijekom postupka sustava Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8226">**HasOpen** – Was document opened during the Office process.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8227">**InstallMethod** – određuje je li sustav nadograđen na trenutačnu međuverziju sustava Office, vraćen na nju ili je u pitanju nova instalacija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8227">**InstallMethod** - Whether the current build of Office was upgraded from, rolled back to, or a fresh install.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8228">**OfficeUILang** – jezik postupka sustava Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8228">**OfficeUILang** – Language of the Office process.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8229">**PreviousBuild** – prethodno instalirana međuverzija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8229">**PreviousBuild** - Previously installed build version.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8230">**SafeMode** – jest postupak sustava Office u sigurnom načinu rada.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8230">**SafeMode** – Was Office process in safe mode.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8231">**SessionId** – jedinstveni identifikator procesa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8231">**SessionId** - A unique identifier of the process.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8232">**SessionInitTime** – Vrijeme pokretanja zahvaćenog procesa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8232">**SessionInitTime** - The time when the affected process started.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8234">Podaci o identitetu korisnika koji su potrebni za ispunjavanje zahtjeva ispitanika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8234">User identity information required to fulfill data subject requests.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8616">**AffectedProcessExeMinorVersion –** broj sporedne verzije zahvaćenog procesa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8616">**AffectedProcessExeMinorVersion -** The Minor Version number of the affected process.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8637">**IsLabMachine –** određuje pokreće li se Office u Microsoftovu laboratoriju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8637">**IsLabMachine -** Whether Office is being run in a Microsoft lab.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8661">**AffectedProcessExeMinorVersion –** broj sporedne verzije zahvaćenog procesa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8661">**AffectedProcessExeMinorVersion -** The Minor Version number of the affected process.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8662">**AffectedProcessExeRevisionVersion –** broj revizije međuverzije zahvaćenog procesa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8662">**AffectedProcessExeRevisionVersion -** The Build Revision Version number of the affected process.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8663">**AffectedProcessIsDebug –** određuje je li međuverzija zahvaćenog procesa verzija za ispravljanje pogrešaka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8663">**AffectedProcessIsDebug -** Whether the affected process is a debug build.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8665">**AffectedProcessOsEnvironment –** identifikator operacijski sustav za zahvaćeni proces.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8665">**AffectedProcessOsEnvironment -** An operating system identifier for the affected process.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8674">**DetectionTime –** vrijeme otkrivanja neočekivanog zatvaranja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8674">**DetectionTime -** The time when the unexpected exit was detected.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8675">**IsLabMachine –** određuje pokreće li se Office u Microsoftovu laboratoriju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8675">**IsLabMachine -** Whether Office is being run in a Microsoft lab.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8676">**IsMsftInternal –** označava je li korisnik sustava Windows koji pokreće Office Microsoftov zaposlenik.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8676">**IsMsftInternal -** Whether the Windows user running Office is a Microsoft employee.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8678">**PreviousLifecycleState –** stanje zahvaćenog procesa kad se srušio.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8678">**PreviousLifecycleState -** The state of the affected process when it crashed.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8679">**UAETypeName –** identifikator grupiranja načina na koji se aplikacija neočekivano zatvorila.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8679">**UAETypeName -** Bucketing identifier for how the app exited ungracefully.</span></span>

### <a name="officesystemsystemhealthungracefulapplicationexitwin32"></a><span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8680">Office.System.SystemHealthUngracefulApplicationExitWin32</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8680">Office.System.SystemHealthUngracefulApplicationExitWin32</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8681">Događaj aktivira nenormalno ukidanje aplikacije (npr. zaustavljanje u upravitelju zadataka, prekid aplikacije, itd.) za klijentske aplikacije sustava Office, kao što su, no ne ograničavajući se na, Word, Excel, PowerPoint i Outlook.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8681">The event is triggers by an abnormal application termination (for example, task manager kill, application hang, etc.) for Office client applications such as, but not limited to, Word, Excel, PowerPoint, and Outlook.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8682">Parametre neočekivanog zatvaranja aplikacije koristimo za mjerenje stanja proizvoda klijenata sustava Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8682">We use Ungraceful Application Exit metrics to measure the health of Office client products.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8683">To je signal ključan za poslovanje koji inženjeri sustava Office koriste za postizanje stabilnosti proizvoda.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8683">It is a business-critical signal used by Office engineers to infer product stability.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8684">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8684">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8685">**AddinExecution –** Zastavica koja obavještava je li izvršavanje dodatka prekinuto prilikom neočekivanog izlaska iz aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8685">**AddinExecution -** Flag that informs if an add-in was executing and didn't finish during an ungraceful application exit.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8686">**BootCompleted –** je li dovršeno pokretanje sustava Office u trenutku rušenja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8686">**BootCompleted –** Was Office boot completed at the time of crash.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8687">**CrashedAppBuild –** identifikator međuverzije zahvaćenog procesa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8687">**CrashedAppBuild -** Build version identifier for the affected process.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8688">**CrashedAppMajor –** identifikator glavne verzije zahvaćenog procesa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8688">**CrashedAppMajor -** Major version identifier for the affected process.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8689">**CrashedAppMinor –** identifikator sporedne verzije zahvaćenog procesa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8689">**CrashedAppMinor -** Minor version identifier for the affected process.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8690">**CrashedAppRevision –** identifikator međuverzije zahvaćenog procesa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8690">**CrashedAppRevision -** Build version identifier for the affected process.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8691">**CrashedEcsETag –** identifikator eksperimenta za srušeni proces.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8691">**CrashedEcsETag -** An experiment identifier for the crashed process.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8692">**CrashedModuleName –** naziv neispravnog modula.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8692">**CrashedModuleName -** Failing module name.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8693">**CrashedSessionId –** jedinstveni identifikator srušenog procesa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8693">**CrashedSessionId -** A unique identifier of the crashed process.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8694">**CrashedSessionInitTime –** vrijeme pokretanja zahvaćenog procesa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8694">**CrashedSessionInitTime -** The time when the affected process started.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8695">**CrashTime –** vrijeme koje ukazuje da je klijent neočekivano prekinut.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8695">**CrashTime –** The time indicating the client terminated ungracefully.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8696">**CrashType –** identifikator grupiranja za vrstu rušenja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8696">**CrashType -** Bucketing identifier for the type of crash.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8697">**DetectionTime –** vrijeme otkrivanja neočekivanog zatvaranja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8697">**DetectionTime -** The time when the unexpected exit was detected.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8698">**ExceptionAddress –** adresa u programu na kojoj je došlo do pogreške.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8698">**ExceptionAddress -** Address in the program where the failure occurred.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8699">**ExceptionCode –** identifikator grupiranja za iznimku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8699">**ExceptionCode -** Bucketing identifier for the exception.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8700">**HandOff –** je li korisnik stvorio i predao Officeov postupak novoj sesiji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8700">**HandOff –** Did the user create and hand off the Office process to a new session.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8701">**HasEdit –** je li korisnik uređivao dokument u srušenom klijentu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8701">**HasEdit –** Was the user editing a document in the crashed client.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8702">**HasOpen –** je li dokument bio otvoren u srušenom klijentu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8702">**HasOpen –** Was a document open in the crashed client.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8703">**HexCrashTag –**  Jedinstveni identifikator kôda rušenja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8703">**HexCrashTag -**  The unique identifier for the code of the crash.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8704">**HexExceptionAddress –** heksadecimalni oblik adrese u programu na kojoj je došlo do pogreške.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8704">**HexExceptionAddress -** Address in hexadecimal in the program where the failure occurred.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8705">**HexExceptionCode –** heksadecimalni identifikator grupiranja za iznimku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8705">**HexExceptionCode -** Bucketing identifier in hexadecimal for the exception.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8706">**HexModuleBaseAddress –** osnovna adresa neispravnog modula u heksadecimalnom obliku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8706">**HexModuleBaseAddress -** Base Address in hexadecimal of the failing module.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8707">**HexModuleBaseAddress –** pomak u bajtovima (u heksadecimalnom obliku) od osnovne adrese na kojoj je došlo do pogreške.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8707">**HexModuleOffset -** Offset in bytes (in hexadecimal) from the base address where the failure occurred.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8708">**HexModuleSize –** veličina neispravnog modula u bajtovima u heksadecimalnom obliku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8708">**HexModuleSize -** Failing module size in bytes in hexadecimal.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8709">**HexVerifyElseCrashTag –** jedinstveni identifikator mjesta na kojem se aplikacija srušila u heksadecimalnom obliku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8709">**HexVerifyElseCrashTag -** Unique identifier in hexadecimal for where the app crashed.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8710">**InstallMethod** – određuje je li sustav nadograđen na trenutnu međuverziju sustava Office, vraćen na nju ili je u pitanju nova instalacija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8710">**InstallMethod -** Whether the current build of Office was upgraded from, rolled back to, or a fresh install.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8711">**IsLabMachine –** određuje pokreće li se Office u Microsoftovu laboratoriju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8711">**IsLabMachine -** Whether Office is being run in a Microsoft lab.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8712">**ModuleBaseAddress –** osnovna adresa neispravnog modula.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8712">**ModuleBaseAddress -** Base Address of the failing module.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8713">**ModuleOffset –** pomak u bajtovima od osnovne adrese na kojoj je došlo do pogreške.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8713">**ModuleOffset -** Offset in bytes from the base address where the failure occurred.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8714">**ModuleSize –** veličina neispravnog modula u bajtovima.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8714">**ModuleSize -** Failing module size in bytes.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8715">**OfficeArchitectureText –** Arhitektura proizvoda sustava Office predstavljena kao niz (npr. x86, arm).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8715">**OfficeArchitectureText -** The architecture of Office product as string (e.g. x86, arm).</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8716">**OfficeUILang –** jezik korisničkog sučelja u međuverziji sustava Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8716">**OfficeUILang –** The language of the User Interface in the Office build.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8717">**PreviousBuild** – prethodno instalirana međuverzija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8717">**PreviousBuild -** Previously installed build version</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8718">**SafeMode –** je li sesija bila pokrenuta u sigurnom načinu rada.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8718">**SafeMode –** Was the session booted in safe mode.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8720">**UninitLibletId –** Jedinstveni identifikator za neispravnu komponentu rušenja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8720">**UninitLibletId –** The unique identifier for the failing component of the crash.</span></span>

### <a name="officesystemungracefulapplicationexitdesktopappexit"></a><span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8723">Office.System.UngracefulApplicationExit.DesktopAppExit</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8723">Office.System.UngracefulApplicationExit.DesktopAppExit</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8724">Koristi se za snimanje metrike rušenja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8724">Used to capture crash metrics.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8725">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8725">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8726">**AppBuildVersion –** identifikator međuverzije zahvaćenog procesa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8726">**AppBuildVersion -** Build version identifier for the affected process.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8727">**AppMajorVersion –** broj glavne verzije zahvaćenog procesa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8727">**AppMajorVersion -** Major Version number of the affected process.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8728">**AppMinorVersion –** identifikator sporedne verzije zahvaćenog procesa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8728">**AppMinorVersion -** Minor version identifier for the affected process.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8729">**AppName –** naziv zahvaćene aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8729">**AppName -** The name of the affected application.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8730">**AppRevisionVersion –** identifikator revizije međuverzije zahvaćenog procesa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8730">**AppRevisionVersion -** Build revision identifier for the affected process.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8731">**CrashedAssignedFlights –** testne verzije dodijeljene srušenom procesu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8731">**CrashedAssignedFlights -** The flights assigned to the crashed process.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8732">**CrashedConfigIds –** konfiguracija dodijeljena srušenom procesu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8732">**CrashedConfigIds -** The configuration assigned to the crashed process.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8733">**CrashedImpressionId –** identifikator prikaza srušenog procesa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8733">**CrashedImpressionId -** The impression identifier of the crashed process.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8734">**CrashedInteractionSessionId –** identifikator sesije interakcije za proces koji se srušio.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8734">**CrashedInteractionSessionId -** The interaction session identifier of the crashed process.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8735">**CrashedProcessSessionId –** jedinstveni identifikator srušenog procesa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8735">**CrashedProcessSessionId -** A unique identifier of the crashed process.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8736">**CrashType –** identifikator grupiranja za vrstu rušenja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8736">**CrashType -** Bucketing identifier for the type of crash.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8737">**ErrorString –** opis pogreške.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8737">**ErrorString -** Error description.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8738">**ExceptionAddress –** adresa u programu na kojoj je došlo do pogreške.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8738">**ExceptionAddress -** Address in the program where the failure occurred.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8739">**ExceptionCode –** identifikator grupiranja za iznimku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8739">**ExceptionCode -** Bucketing identifier for the exception.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8740">**FaultAppName –** naziv aplikacije s pogreškom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8740">**FaultAppName -** The name of the faulting app.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8741">**InstallMethod** – određuje je li sustav nadograđen na trenutnu međuverziju sustava Office, vraćen na nju ili je u pitanju nova instalacija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8741">**InstallMethod -** Whether the current build of Office was upgraded from, rolled back to, or a fresh install.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8743">**IsDebug –** označava radi li se o međuverziji sustava Office za ispravljanje pogrešaka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8743">**IsDebug -** Whether this is a debug build of Office.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8744">**IsHandledCrash –** određuje je li u sesiji koja se srušila aktiviran rukovatelj rušenja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8744">**IsHandledCrash -** Whether the crash handler was invoked in the crashing session.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8745">**IsLabMachine –** određuje pokreće li se Office u Microsoftovu laboratoriju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8745">**IsLabMachine -** Whether Office is being run in a Microsoft lab.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8746">**ModuleBaseAddress –** osnovna adresa neispravnog modula.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8746">**ModuleBaseAddress -** Base Address of the failing module.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8747">**ModuleName –** naziv neispravnog modula.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8747">**ModuleName -** Failing module name.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8748">**ModuleOffset –** pomak u bajtovima od osnovne adrese na kojoj je došlo do pogreške.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8748">**ModuleOffset -** Offset in bytes from the base address where the failure occurred.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8749">**ModuleSize –** veličina neispravnog modula u bajtovima.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8749">**ModuleSize -** Failing module size in bytes.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8750">**OSEnvironment –** identifikator okruženja u kojem je Office pokrenut.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8750">**OSEnvironment -** Identifier for what environment Office is running on.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8751">**PreviousBuild** – prethodno instalirana međuverzija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8751">**PreviousBuild -** Previously installed build version</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8752">**PreviousInteractionSessionTime –** vrijeme pokretanja prethodne sesije interakcije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8752">**PreviousInteractionSessionTime -** Time which the previous interaction session started.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8753">**PreviousLifecycleState –** identifikator stanja životnog ciklusa prethodne sesije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8753">**PreviousLifecycleState -** Previous session lifecycle state identifier.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8754">**PreviousSessionInitTime –** vrijeme pokretanja prethodne sesije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8754">**PreviousSessionInitTime -** Time when the previous session started.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8755">**StackHash –** identifikator koji označava gdje se u kodu zahvaćeni proces srušio.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8755">**StackHash -** An identifier indicating where in code that the affected process crashed.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8756">**VerifyElseCrashTag –** jedinstveni identifikator mjesta na kojem se aplikacija srušila.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8756">**VerifyElseCrashTag -** Unique identifier for where the app crashed.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8945">**LatencyLE200** – broj prijenosa čije je kašnjenje manje od 200 ms.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8945">**LatencyLE200** - The number of uploads with a latency less than 200 milliseconds.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8946">**MaxLatency** – najveće zabilježeno kašnjenje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8946">**MaxLatency** - The highest latency observed.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="72c2f-8947">**MinLatency** – najmanje zabilježeno kašnjenje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-8947">**MinLatency** - The lowest latency observed.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72c2f-9039">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72c2f-9039">The following fields are collected:</span></span>
